Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.77,0:02:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦先生  请描述\NMr. Dufresne, describe...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.94,0:02:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,命案当晚你和妻子争吵的情形\Nthe confrontation you had with your wife the night she was murdered.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们吵得很凶\NIt was very bitter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.95,0:02:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她说不怕我知道  她讨厌偷偷摸摸\NShe said she was glad I knew,that she hated all the sneaking around.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.82,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她还说  想去雷诺市办离婚\NAnd she said that she wanted a divorce in Reno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.56,0:02:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}-你怎样回答?  -我拒绝离婚\N-What was your response?  -I told her I would not grant one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.43,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}“你休想活着去雷诺市。”\N"I'll see you in hell before I see you in Reno."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.80,0:02:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邻居作证你说过这句话\NThose were your words, according to your neighbors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许吧\NIf they say so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我气炸了  记不清楚\NI really don't remember. I was upset.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}你们吵完以后呢？\NWhat happened after you argued with your wife?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她收拾行李\NShe packed a bag.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去跟昆汀住……\NShe packed a bag to go and stay with Mr. Quentin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.48,0:02:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}格伦·昆汀  乡村俱乐部的高尔夫球教练\NGlenn Quentin, golf pro at the Snowden Hills Country Club...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.79,0:03:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}你最近才发现  他是你太太的情夫\Nwhom you had discovered was your wife's lover.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你跟踪她吗？\NDid you follow her?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先去酒吧买醉\NI went to a few bars first.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.07,0:03:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}然后去他家  但没人在\NLater, I drove to his house to confront them. They weren't home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我停了车\NI parked in the turnout...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等他们\Nand waited.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用意何在？\NWith what intention?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不确定\NI'm not sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.28,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}我醉了\NI was confused...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}糊里糊涂\Ndrunk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想……\NI think...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最多只是吓吓他们\Nmostly I wanted to scare them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果他们一回来  你就冲进屋杀了他们\NWhen they arrived, you went up to the house and murdered them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不  我逐渐酒醒\NI was sobering up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.26,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开车回家睡觉\NI got back in the car and I drove home to sleep it off.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}路中把枪丢入皇家河\NAlong the way, I threw my gun into the Royal River.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1}我已讲得很清楚\NI've been very clear on this point.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但清洁妇隔天早晨上工时\NI get hazy where the cleaning woman shows up the following morning...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an3}发现床上的二人尸体\Nand finds your wife in bed with her lover...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an3}身上满是点三八的弹孔\Nriddled with.38-caliber bullets.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.08,0:04:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不觉得这很巧吗？  还是只有我这么想？\NDoes that strike you as a fantastic coincidence, or is it just me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是很巧\NYes, it does.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.39,0:04:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an4}但你仍声称早在案发之前\NYet you still maintain you threw your gun into the river...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an4}就已丢弃了枪\Nbefore the murders took place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种说法倒是很省事\NThat's very convenient.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是实话\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,警方打捞三天都没找到\NThe police dragged that river for three days, and nary a gun was found...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.23,0:04:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}这样就无法比对你的手枪和\Nso no comparison could be made between your gun and the bullets...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.64,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从受害人血尸内取出的弹头\Ntaken from the bloodstained corpses of the victims.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以呢\NAnd that also...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样也非常省事  不是吗  杜弗伦先生\Nis very convenient. Isn't it, Mr. Dufresne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是清白的\NSince I am innocent of this crime...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.59,0:04:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以找不到枪  反倒对我非常不利\NI find it decidedly inconvenient that the gun was never found.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.11,0:05:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切证据都向各位指明了案情\NLadies and gentlemen, you've heard all the evidence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.68,0:05:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,脚印和胎痕证明被告在场\NWe have the accused at the scene of the crime. We have footprints.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,散落地面的子弹上有他的指纹\NBullets on the ground bearing his fingerprints.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an6}酒瓶碎片上同样也有指痕\NA broken bourbon bottle, likewise with fingerprints.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an6}最重要的是\NAnd most of all...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an6}一位美女与情夫\Nwe have a beautiful young woman and her lover...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相拥而死\Nlying dead in each other's arms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an3}他们是有伤风化\NThey had sinned.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an3}但是\NBut was their crime so great...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an3}罪该致死吗？\Nas to merit a death sentence?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与此同时  请各位\NWhile you think about that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再考虑一件事\Nthink about this:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一只左轮手枪只能装六发子弹  而非八发\NA revolver holds six bullets, not eight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.03,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}所以他并非一时冲动\NI submit that this was not a hot-blooded crime of passion.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.49,0:05:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}冲动即使不可宽恕  但尚可理解\NThat at least could be understood, if not condoned.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然而\NNo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是复仇\NThis was revenge...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.06,0:05:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,残忍而冷血的谋杀  想想看\Nof a much more brutal, cold-blooded nature. Consider this:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这两人各中四枪\NFour bullets per victim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,共八枪  而非六枪\NNot six shots fired, but eight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.07,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此他是先射完一轮\NThat means that he fired the gun empty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.91,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再装弹补上两枪\Nand then stopped to reload so that he could shoot each of them again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一人添一枪\NAn extra bullet per lover...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,射入脑袋\Nright in the head.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.35,0:06:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你面目冷漠  全无悔意  杜弗伦先生\NYou strike me as a particularly icy and remorseless man, Mr. Dufresne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看见你就令我齿冷\NIt chills my blood just to look at you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据缅因州赋予我的权力\NBy the power vested in me by the state of Maine...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我判处你两次终身监禁\NI hereby order you to serve two life sentences back-to-back...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分别为两位死者偿命  退庭！\None for each of your victims. So be it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坐下\NSit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.60,0:07:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据你的材料 你的终身监禁已经服满20年\NWe see you've served 20 years of a life sentence?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-是的  -你改过自新了吗？\N-Yes, sir.  -You feel you've been rehabilitated?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.98,0:07:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的  完全改造好了\NYes, sir. Absolutely, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是说  我已吸取教训\NI mean, I learned my lesson.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.78,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的  我已洗心革面\NI can honestly say that I'm a changed man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会再做危害社会的事了\NI'm no longer a danger to society.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.03,0:07:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我向上帝发誓\NThat's God's honest truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德\NHey, Red.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎样？\NHow'd it go?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不是老样子\NSame old shit, different day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解\NYeah, I know how you feel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我下周也准备要吃闭门羹\NI'm up for rejection next week.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.58,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我上周才假释被拒\NYeah, I got rejected last week.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很正常\NIt happens.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨，瑞德，借一包烟吧\NHey, Red, bump me a deck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,滚开  你欠我五包了\NGet out of my face, man! You're into me for five packs already.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-四包  -五包\N-Four!  -Five!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美国每个监狱里可能都会有我这样的人\NThere must be a con like me in every prison in America.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能为你弄到各种东西\NI'm the guy who can get it for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,香烟啦  大麻啦\NCigarettes, a bag of reefer, if that's your thing...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.03,0:08:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孩子高中毕业想喝白兰地也行\Nbottle of brandy to celebrate your kid's high school graduation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你想  几乎都没问题\NDamn near anything within reason.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 先生  我就像百货公司\NYes, sir! I'm a regular Sears and Roebuck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.68,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以1949年当安迪·杜弗伦来找我\NSo when Andy Dufresne came to me in 1949...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问能否弄张丽塔·海华丝的海报进来时\Nand asked me to smuggle Rita Hayworth into the prison for him...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我二话不说  “没问题！”\NI told him, "No problem."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.90,0:09:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到大门口集合\Nto the main gate
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到大门口集合\Nto the main gate
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪在47年初进肖申克监狱\NAndy came to Shawshank Prison...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.13,0:09:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,罪名是杀害老婆和情夫\Nin early 1947 for murdering his wife and the fella she was banging.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.33,0:09:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他原本是缅因州一家大银行的副总裁\NOn the outside, he'd been vice president of a large Portland bank.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,年轻有为  前程远大\NGood work for a man so young.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来这里  瑞德\NHere, Red.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听得懂英语吗？\NYou speak English, butt-steak?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟这位长官走\NYou follow this officer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.47,0:11:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我这辈子没看过这么多满脸晦气的窝囊废\NI never seen such a sorry-Iooking heap of maggot shit in all my life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菜鸟  过来\NHey, fish! Come over here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打个赌吧  瑞德？\NTaking bets today, Red?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赌烟还是赌钱？\NSmokes or coin? Bettor's choice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烟  我赌两根\NSmokes. Put me down for two.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你挑哪个？\NAll right, who's your horse?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个小个子\NThat little sack of shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.87,0:11:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-前面排第八  他会是第一个  -算你瞎眼  我赌了\N-Eighth. He'll be first.  -Bullshit! I'll take that action.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输定了\NYou're out some smokes, son.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你聪明  你挑呀\NIf you're so smart, you call it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胖脸肥臀那个\NI'll take that chubby fat-ass there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第五个  我赌五根烟\NThe fifth one. Put me down for a quarter deck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,头名菜鸟大选日\NFresh fish today!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们又有的玩啦\NWe're reeling them in!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.43,0:12:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说实话  当初我并不看好他\NI admit I didn't think much of Andy first time I laid eyes on him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.63,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弱不禁风\NLooked like a stiff breeze would blow him over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是他给我的最初印象\NThat was my first impression of the man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你挑谁？\NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面带富贵相的高个儿\NThat tall drink of water with the silver spoon up his ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他？  不可能啦\NThat guy? Never happen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我赌十根烟  -有种\N-10 cigarettes.  -That's a rich bet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁要和我赌？\NWho's going to prove me wrong?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赫伍？  渣哥？\NHeywood? Jigger?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,史基？\NSkeets?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,福洛？\NFloyd!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们输定了\NFour brave souls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回牢房准备点名\NReturn to your cellblocks for evening count.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都回牢房\NAll prisoners, return to your cellblocks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向右转\NTurn to the right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.55,0:12:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向前看\NEyes front.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是看守长海利\NThis is Mr. Hadley. He's captain of the guards.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是典狱长诺顿\NI'm Mr. Norton, the warden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们被判有罪\NYou are convicted felons.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以被送到这来\NThat's why they've sent you to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一条规矩\NRule number one:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.71,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不许亵渎上帝\NNo blasphemy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.71,0:13:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里不准滥呼上帝之名\NI'll not have the Lord's name taken in vain in my prison.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其它规矩……\NThe other rules...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们以后就知道了  有问题吗？\Nyou'll figure out as you go along. Any questions?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.42,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么时候吃饭？\NWhen do we eat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们叫你吃就吃\NYou eat when we say you eat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫你拉就拉  叫你撒就撒\NYou shit when we say you shit, and piss when we say you piss.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听明白了吗？人渣\NYou got that, you maggot-dick motherfucker?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站起来\NOn your feet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只相信两件事\NI believe in two things:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.11,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纪律和圣经\NDiscipline and the Bible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两样都少不了\NHere, you'll receive both.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把信仰寄托神\NPut your trust in the Lord.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把贱命交给我\NYour ass belongs to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肖申克监狱欢迎各位\NWelcome to Shawshank.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,解铐\NUnhook them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,转身\NTurn around.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以了\NThat's enough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到笼子边上去\NMove to the end of the cage.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,转身  洒除虱粉\NTurn around. Delouse him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,转身\NTurn around.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出来  去领囚衣和圣经\NMove out of the cage. Pick up your clothes and Bible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一个\NNext man up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向右\NTo the right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,右转  右转\NRight. Right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向左\NLeft.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,头一夜最难熬  绝对如此\NThe first night's the toughest. No doubt about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光着屁股行进  像刚出生时那样\NThey march you in naked as the day you were born...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火辣的药粉令你半盲\Nskin burning and half-blind from that delousing shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当你进了囚笼……\NAnd when they put you in that cell...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,门闸锁上……\Nand those bars slam home...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.86,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你才明白这是玩真的\Nthat's when you know it's for real.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眨眼间  一生就毁了\NOld life blown away in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.16,0:15:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只留下无穷的悔恨\NNothing left but all the time in the world to think about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.34,0:15:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新来的初到之夜多半崩溃\NMost new fish come close to madness the first night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总会有人哭出来\NSomebody always breaks down crying.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫无例外\NHappens every time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯一的问题是\NThe only question is...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁会是第一个\Nwho's it going to be?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.25,0:15:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用这聚赌也挺有趣的\NIt's as good a thing to bet on as any, I guess.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我赌安迪·杜弗伦\NI had my money on Andy Dufresne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熄灯\NLights out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还记得我来这的第一晚\NI remember my first night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然那已经是很久很久以前的事了\NSeems like a long time ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菜鸟  来嘛\NHey, fish.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菜鸟  菜鸟\NFish, fish.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么  怕黑吗？\NWhat are you, scared of the dark?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后悔爸妈搞你出来？\NBet you wish your daddy never dicked your mama!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小猪猪  你的肉好香\NPiggy! Pork! I want me a pork chop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.26,0:16:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老鸟总是捉弄菜鸟\NThe boys always go fishing with first-timers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到惹哭才罢休\NAnd they don't quit till they reel someone in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猪公\NHey, Fat Ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肥臀\NFat Ass!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说句话嘛\NTalk to me, boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我听得到你喘气\NI know you're there. I can hear you breathing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.11,0:17:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别理这些蠢货\NDon't you listen to these nitwits, you hear me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这儿没那么糟啦\NThis place ain't so bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.61,0:17:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟你讲\NTell you what...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会帮你引见  带你过家家\NI'll introduce you around, make you feel right at home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道有些个同志\NI know a couple of big old bull queers that'd just...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会乐意亲近你\NIove to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.16,0:17:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尤其你那白肉肥臀\NEspecially that big, white, mushy butt of yours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天哪\NGod!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要坐牢\NI don't belong here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-有人中奖了  -我要回家\N-We have a winner!  -I want to go home!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.34,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肥臀中得头名\NAnd it's Fat Ass by a nose!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,头名菜鸟！  头名菜鸟！\NFresh fish! Fresh fish!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不属于这里\NI don't belong here
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要回家\NI want to go home!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要见我妈妈\NI want my mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我搞过你妈  不够爽\NI had your mother! She wasn't that great!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天杀的  你们在搞什么鬼？\NWhat the Christ is this horseshit?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你亵渎上帝  我要报告监狱长\NHe blasphemed. I'll tell the warden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.00,0:18:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你菊花插上警棍再去告我吧！\NYou'll tell him with my baton up your ass!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放我出去！\NLet me out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.63,0:18:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发什么神经，你这混蛋肥猪\NWhat is your malfunction, you fat barrel of monkey spunk?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.24,0:18:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你！  我本不该在这里！\NPlease! I ain't supposed to be here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不该是我！\NNot me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想数到三  连一我都不去数\NI won't count to three. Not even to one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上给我闭嘴  不然就给你来段“催眠曲”\NYou shut up, or I'll sing you a lullaby!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快闭嘴 不然就完了\NShut up, man. Shut up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们弄错了  我不该坐牢的\NYou don't understand.  I'm not supposed to be here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开门\NOpen that cell.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不该在这里  这儿被他们搞得像座他妈的监狱！\NMe neither! They run this place like a fucking prison!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.03,0:18:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狗娘养的\NSon of a bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长官  别激动\NCaptain, take it easy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.33,0:19:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚  再有谁敢哀嚎\NIf I hear so much as a mouse fart in here tonight...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.80,0:19:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就扁得你们全部躺进医务室\NI swear by God and Jesus, you will all visit the infirmary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.74,0:19:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人人有份\NEvery last motherfucker in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.48,0:19:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把这废人抬去医务室\NCall the trustees. Take that tub of shit down to the infirmary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.50,0:19:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪头一夜就害我输了两包烟\NHis first night in the joint, Dufresne cost me two packs of cigarettes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他一声都没吭\NHe never made a sound.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,北三层  到齐\NTier 3 north, clear count!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南二层  到齐\NTier 2 north, clear count.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.26,0:20:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南三层  到齐\NTier 3 south, clear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南一层  到齐\NTier 1 south, clear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南四层  到齐\NTier 4 south, clear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备\NPrepare to roll out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出发\NRoll out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要吃吗？\NAre you going to eat that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.86,0:21:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无此打算\NI hadn't planned on it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能给我吗？\NDo you mind?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又肥又嫩\NThat's nice and ripe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.19,0:21:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杰克说  谢谢你\NJake says thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.76,0:21:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它从巢中掉到地上\NFell out of his nest over by the plate shop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.36,0:22:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要养到它会飞\NI'm going to look after him until he's big enough to fly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌  他来了\NOh, no! Here he comes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.01,0:22:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安  伙计们\NMorning, fellas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.67,0:22:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是个美好早晨啊\NFine morning, isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.94,0:22:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道为何如此美好吗？\NYou know why it's a fine morning, don't you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.45,0:22:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烟拿出来  就地排好\NSend them down. I want them lined up...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.95,0:22:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像合唱队一样排整齐\Njust like a pretty little chorus line.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.62,0:22:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真壮观\NLook at that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.35,0:22:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-真受不了他  -我的乖乖\N-I can't stand this guy.  -Oh, Lord!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.19,0:22:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错  正宗吉时香烟\NYes! Richmond, Virginia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.86,0:22:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闻我的屁吧\NSmell my ass!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.43,0:22:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闻完再闻我的\NAfter he smells mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.86,0:22:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德  可惜你大大看走眼\NThat's a shame about your horse coming in last and all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过我真感谢我的猪公\NBut I sure do love that winning horse of mine, though.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.80,0:22:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出院后我得亲亲他\NI owe that boy a big kiss when I see him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.97,0:22:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请他抽烟才对  小人得志\NWhy don't you give him some of your cigarettes instead? Lucky fuck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.48,0:22:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘿  泰瑞\NHey, Tyrell.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.38,0:22:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这周你在医务室值班吗？\NYou pull infirmary duty this week?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.32,0:22:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那肥仔怎样了？\NHow's my horse doing anyway?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.32,0:22:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挂了\NDead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海利打爆了他的头\NHadley busted his head up pretty good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.69,0:23:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,医生回家睡觉了\NDoc had gone home for the night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.39,0:23:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他一直僵到天亮\NPoor bastard lay there till this morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.86,0:23:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本无药可救\NBy then, there wasn't nothing we could do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.64,0:23:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他叫什么名字？\NWhat was his name?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.31,0:23:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？\NWhat'd you say?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想知道他的名字\NI was just wondering if anyone knew his name.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关你屁事  菜鸟\NWhat the fuck do you care, new fish?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.32,0:23:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死人还关心什么名字\NDoesn't fucking matter what his name was. He's dead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.03,0:23:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘿\NHey
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.51,0:23:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人上过你了吗？\NAnybody come at you yet?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.65,0:24:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你名草有主了吗？\NAnybody get to you yet?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牢里人人需要朋友\NHey, we all need friends in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.99,0:24:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以当你朋友\NI could be a friend to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.86,0:24:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不易上手\NHard to get.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.37,0:24:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正合我意\NI like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.81,0:24:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起初安迪不与人来往\NAndy kept pretty much to himself at first.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.38,0:24:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概心事重重\NI guess he had a lot on his mind...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.78,0:24:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,努力适应牢狱生活\Ntrying to adapt to life on the inside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.35,0:24:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到一个月后\NWasn't until a month went by before he opened his mouth...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.76,0:24:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他主动才找人攀谈\Nto say more than two words to somebody.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.33,0:24:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个人……\NAs it turned out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.36,0:24:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是我\Nthat somebody was me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.01,0:24:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫安迪·杜弗伦\NI'm Andy Dufresne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.01,0:25:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀妻的银行家\NWife-killing banker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.98,0:25:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了什么？\NWhy'd you do it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.75,0:25:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没犯罪\NI didn't, since you ask.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.42,0:25:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你来对地方了\NYou're going to fit right in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.49,0:25:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里人人都无罪\NEverybody in here's innocent. Didn't you know that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.39,0:25:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-赫伍  你为何入狱？  -我无罪  被律师害了\N-What you in here for?  -Didn't do it. Lawyer fucked me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.03,0:25:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说你颇爱耍酷\NRumor has it you're a real cold fish.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.80,0:25:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道你的屁比别人香？\NYou think your shit smells sweeter than most. Is that right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.60,0:25:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说呢？\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.44,0:25:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说老实话  我还不清楚\NTo tell you the truth, I haven't made up my mind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.64,0:25:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你很有办法\NI understand you're a man that knows how to get things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.41,0:25:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能够让你有求必应\NI'm known to locate certain things from time to time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.91,0:25:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想要一把石锤\NI wonder if you might get me a rock hammer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.88,0:25:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.25,0:25:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石锤\NA rock hammer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.85,0:25:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-用来干什么？  -何必问呢？\N-What is it and why?  -What do you care?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.89,0:25:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是牙刷  我就直接报价\NFor a toothbrush, I wouldn't ask. I'd quote a price.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.79,0:25:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为牙刷不危险  对吗？\NBut a toothbrush is a non-lethal object, isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.80,0:25:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也有道理\NFair enough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.63,0:26:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石锤大约六、七寸长\NA rock hammer is about six or seven inches long.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.47,0:26:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-像鹤嘴锄  -鹤嘴锄？\N-Looks like a miniature pickax.  -Pickax?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.00,0:26:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敲石头用的\NFor rocks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.81,0:26:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石英？\NQuartz?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.04,0:26:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石英\NQuartz
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.98,0:26:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,云母  页岩……\NAnd some mica, shale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.69,0:26:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石灰石\Nlimestone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.19,0:26:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以呢？\NSo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.26,0:26:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾是石痴\NSo I'm a rock hound.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.52,0:26:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想重拾往日嗜好\NAt least I was in my old life. I'd like to be again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.89,0:26:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看你是想捶人家脑袋\NOr maybe you'd like to sink your toy into somebody's skull.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.50,0:26:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的  这儿没人犯着我\NNo, I have no enemies here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.27,0:26:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有？  且慢\NNo? Wait a while.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.20,0:26:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话已传开了\NWord gets around.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.47,0:26:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三姐妹对你有性趣\NThe Sisters have taken quite a liking to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.34,0:26:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尤其是伯格斯\NEspecially Bogs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.15,0:26:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算跟他们说我不是同性恋也没用吗\NDon't suppose it would help if I told them I'm not homosexual.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.78,0:26:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们也不是\NNeither are they.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.42,0:26:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同性恋是人  但他们是畜牲\NYou have to be human first. They don't qualify.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.39,0:27:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想干就干  根本不在乎你\NBull queers take by force. That's all they want or understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.00,0:27:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我若是你  便会加倍提防\NIf I were you, I'd grow eyes in the back of my head.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.74,0:27:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-谢谢你的忠告  -反正不用钱\N-Thanks for the advice.  -Well, that's free.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.84,0:27:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你明白我的顾虑吧\NYou understand my concern.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.01,0:27:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不用石锤惹事  行吗？\NIf there's trouble, I won't use the rock hammer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.51,0:27:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你想逃狱  挖地道？\NThen I'd guess you want to escape. Tunnel under the wall, maybe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.45,0:27:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么好笑？\NWhat did I miss?  What's so funny?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.55,0:27:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看到它就明白了\NYou'll understand when you see the rock hammer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.09,0:27:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它市价多少？\NWhat's an item like this usually go for?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.52,0:27:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇石店卖七美元\NSeven dollars in any rock-and-gem shop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.53,0:27:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我通常加两成\NMy normal markup's 20 percent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:35.20,0:27:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过特殊东西嘛\NBut this is a specialty item.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.77,0:27:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风险越大  价钱越高  一口价  十美元吧\NRisk goes up, price goes up. Let's make it an even 10 bucks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.44,0:27:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样\NTen it is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.51,0:27:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实你是白花钱\NWaste of money, if you ask me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.81,0:27:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？\NWhy's that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:50.51,0:27:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狱方喜欢突击检查\NFolks around this joint love surprise inspections.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.15,0:27:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发现石锤一定没收\NThey find it, you're going to lose it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.32,0:27:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时候别把我供出来\NIf they catch you, you don't know me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.62,0:28:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否则再也别想跟我做生意\NMention my name, we never do business again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.36,0:28:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连口香糖都不卖给你  明白了吗\NNot for shoelaces or a stick of gum. Now you got that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.29,0:28:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂的\NI understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.06,0:28:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢  你叫……\NThank you, Mr...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.37,0:28:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德\NRed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.93,0:28:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫我瑞德\NName's Red.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.10,0:28:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德\NRed
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.87,0:28:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为何叫瑞德？\NWhy do they call you that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.28,0:28:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许因为我是爱尔兰人吧\NMaybe it's because I'm Irish.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.45,0:28:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪不得有人认为他臭屁\NI could see why some of the boys took him for snobby.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.19,0:28:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他闷声不响\NHe had a quiet way about him...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:37.96,0:28:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,步伐和谈吐简直异类\Na walk and a talk that just wasn't normal around here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.46,0:28:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像……\NHe strolled...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.13,0:28:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在公园散步  无忧无虑\Nlike a man in the park without a care or a worry in the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:48.54,0:28:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仿佛身披隐形衣\NLike he had on an invisible coat that would shield him from this place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.71,0:28:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错\Nyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.14,0:28:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我打一开始\NI think it'd be fair to say...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.65,0:28:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就喜欢他\NI liked Andy from the start.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:01.48,0:29:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别磨蹭  屁股后还有一大堆事呢\NLet's go! Some of us got a schedule to keep.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.56,0:29:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点  快点\NMove it! Come on, move it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.66,0:29:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近怎样？  你老婆待你还好吗？\NHow you doing? How's the wife treating you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:28.28,0:29:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,继续走\NKeep moving.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.18,0:29:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,继续走\NJust go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.52,0:29:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德\NRed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.74,0:29:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪说的对\NAndy was right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:56.44,0:29:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,见到货我就明白了\NI finally got the joke.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.97,0:30:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用它挖地道\NIt would take a man about 600 years...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.58,0:30:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得挖六百年\Nto tunnel under the wall with one of these.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.82,0:30:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-要书吗？  -不要\N-Book?  -Not today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:16.29,0:30:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-要书吗？  -不要\N-Book? -Not
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.73,0:30:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老布\NBrook
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.63,0:30:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给杜弗伦的货\NDelivery for Dufresne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.91,0:30:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要书吗？\NBook?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:37.61,0:30:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要书吗？\NBook?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.28,0:30:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦\NDufresne
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.54,0:30:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的书\NHere's your book.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.09,0:30:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.57,0:31:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦  漂白粉不够了  你去后面拿点\NWe're running low on hexite. Get on back and fetch us up some.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.61,0:31:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这东西会弄瞎你的眼\NThis will blind you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.54,0:31:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宝贝  嘘\NHoney, hush.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.49,0:31:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反抗\NThat's it. You fight!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.66,0:32:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才刺激\NBetter that way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.37,0:32:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也希望会是另一种结局\NI wish I could tell you Andy fought the good fight...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.67,0:32:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是安迪打赢  全身而退\Nand the Sisters let him be.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.24,0:32:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望如此\NI wish I could tell you that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.28,0:32:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然而监狱不是童话世界\Nbut prison is no fairy-tale world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.38,0:32:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他从没说过是谁干的\NHe never said who did it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.58,0:32:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但谁都明白\NBut we all knew.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.02,0:32:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日子就这样一天天过去\NThings went on like that for a while.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.93,0:32:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,监狱生活就像例行公事\NPrison life consists of routine...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:34.70,0:32:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除此之外还是例行公事\Nand then more routine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:39.17,0:32:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪常常挂上新伤\NEvery so often, Andy would show up with fresh bruises.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.17,0:32:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三姐妹不放过他\NThe Sisters kept at him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.24,0:32:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他有时打赢\NSometimes he was able to fight them off.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:48.51,0:32:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时吃败仗\NSometimes not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.18,0:32:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是安迪的监狱生活\NAnd that's how it went for Andy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.92,0:32:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是他的例行公事\NThat was his routine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.52,0:32:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信最初那两年是他最糟糕的\NI do believe those first two years were the worst for him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.46,0:33:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也相信日子再这样下去\NAnd I also believe that if things had gone on that way...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.16,0:33:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这地方早晚会把他毁了\Nthis place would have got the best of him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.36,0:33:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是  在1949年的春天\NBut then, in the spring of 1949...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.36,0:33:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上头决定\Nthe powers that be decided:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.47,0:33:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车牌厂的屋顶需要翻修\NThe roof of the license-plate factory needs resurfacing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.00,0:33:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我需要12名自愿者劳作一周\NI need a dozen volunteers for a week's work.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.91,0:33:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们都知道\NAs you know...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.11,0:33:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特别的公差享有特别的待遇\Nspecial detail carries with it special privileges.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.88,0:33:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是户外公差\NIt was outdoor detail...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.68,0:33:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而五月是户外活动的好时间\Nand May is one damned fine month to be working outdoors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.25,0:33:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,排好队\NStay in line there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.72,0:33:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一百多人志愿报名\NMore than a hundred men volunteered for the job.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.16,0:33:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昂格\NWallace E. Unger.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:45.67,0:33:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞丁\NEllis Redding.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.24,0:33:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是很巧吗？\NWouldn't you know it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:50.24,0:33:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的哥们全都中签\NMe and some fellows I know were among the names called.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.74,0:33:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪·杜弗伦\NAndrew Dufresne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.14,0:33:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实是每人一包烟买的\NIt only cost us a pack of smokes per man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.58,0:34:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我照常抽两成\NI made my usual 20 percent, of course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:02.25,0:34:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,德州一个律师打电话来\NSo this big-shot lawyer calls me long-distance from Texas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.92,0:34:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我问  “什么事？”\NI say, "Yeah?"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.76,0:34:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说  “抱歉，令兄过世。”\NHe says, "Sorry to inform you, but your brother just died."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.59,0:34:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我很遗憾  -我才不为那烂人遗憾\N-I'm sorry to hear that.  -I'm not. He was an asshole.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.70,0:34:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他离家多年  早就当他死了\NRan off years ago. Figured him for dead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.10,0:34:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位大律师说\NSo this lawyer fellow says to me:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:20.60,0:34:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“令兄是位富翁。”  挖油井赚了一百万\N"He died a rich man." Oil wells and shit. Close to a million bucks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.41,0:34:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一百万？\NA million bucks?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.58,0:34:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-对  算他走狗运  -有你一份吗?\N-Incredible how lucky some assholes get.  -You going to see any of that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:32.68,0:34:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他留给我三万五\NThirty-five thousand. That's what he left me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.65,0:34:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-美金？  -对\NDollars?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.59,0:34:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,简直像中乐透嘛\NThat's great! That's like winning the sweepstakes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.92,0:34:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是吗？\NIsn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.22,0:34:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,政府是白混的吗？\NDumb shit, what do you think the government will do to me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.39,0:34:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它想大口分掉这大饼\NTake a big wet bite out of my ass is what.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.53,0:34:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怜虫\NPoor Byron.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.77,0:34:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过路财神  真够倒霉\NTerrible fucking luck, huh? Crying shame.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.14,0:34:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人就是命衰\NSome people really got it awful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.67,0:34:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你疯了？\NAndy, are you nuts?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.24,0:35:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,专心干活\NIKeep your eyes on your mop, man!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.34,0:35:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,缴了税还剩不少\NYou'll pay some tax, but you'll still end up...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.51,0:35:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错  够换新车\NYeah, maybe enough to buy a new car, and then what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.51,0:35:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但买车要缴税\NI got to pay tax on the car. Repair...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.92,0:35:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还要修理  保养  孩子吵着要兜风\Nmaintenance, kids pestering you to take them for a ride all the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.89,0:35:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万一报错税  全得自付\NThen if you figure your tax wrong, you pay out of your own pocket.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.76,0:35:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告诉你  这就是山姆大叔\NI tell you! Uncle Sam!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:19.13,0:35:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石头都榨得出血来\NHe puts his hand in your shirt and squeezes your tit till it's purple.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.46,0:35:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪！\NAndy! Andy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.77,0:35:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-他在找死  -继续干活\N-Getting himself killed. -I Keep tarring.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.17,0:35:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么哥哥  狗屁！\NSome brother. Shit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.64,0:35:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海利先生\NMr. Hadley...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.91,0:35:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你信任老婆吗？\Ndo you trust your wife?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.92,0:35:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真好笑\NOh, that's funny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.92,0:35:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没了牙给我吹喇叭更好笑\NYou'll look funnier sucking my dick with no teeth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.75,0:35:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她会扯你后腿吗？\NWhat I mean is, do you think she'd go behind your back?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:50.22,0:35:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,够了  他活得不耐烦了\NStep aside, Mert. This fucker's having himself an accident.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:53.83,0:35:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他要推落安迪！\NHe'll push him off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:55.10,0:35:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她要是靠得住\NIf you trust her, you can keep...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.16,0:35:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就能领三万五\Nthat 35,000.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.30,0:36:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你说什么？  -三万五\N-What did you say?  -Thirty-five thousand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.64,0:36:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部领到\NAll of it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:03.87,0:36:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-一个子儿也不少  -你最好别耍我\N-Every penny.  -You better start making sense.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.14,0:36:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想领全额  就赠与太太\NIf you want to keep it,  give it to your wife.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.68,0:36:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国税局允许一生一次  最多六万的赠与免税\NThe IRS allows a one-time-only gift to your spouse for up to $ 60,000.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:13.78,0:36:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-乖乖  免税？  -对\N-Bullshit. Tax-free?  -Tax-free.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.35,0:36:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国税局征不到一文钱\NIRS can't touch one cent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.72,0:36:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是那个杀妻的银行家？\NYou're that smart banker that killed his wife.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.42,0:36:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,信你难道不会害我坐牢？\NWhy should I believe you? So I can end up in here with you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.99,0:36:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全合法  你去问国税局也一样\NIt's legal. Ask the IRS. They'll say the same thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.03,0:36:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不该开口的  我以为你会去问\NI feel stupid telling you this. I'm sure you would have investigated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.30,0:36:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不用你教我这些鸟事\NI don't need you to tell me where the bear shit in the buckwheat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.17,0:36:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错  但你要找人填表\NOf course not. But you do need someone to set it up for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.77,0:36:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请律师可得花钱\NThat'll cost you. A lawyer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.54,0:36:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没卵的讼棍\NA bunch of ball-washing bastards!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.28,0:36:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我帮你办  给你省钱\NI suppose I could set it up for you. That would save you some money.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.95,0:36:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你领表我来填\NYou get the forms, I'll prepare them...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.25,0:36:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全免费\Nnearly free of charge.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.22,0:36:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要请我同事一人三瓶啤酒\NI'd only ask three beers apiece for each of my coworkers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.49,0:36:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“同事”？  够新鲜的\N"Coworkers." That's rich!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.86,0:37:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做黑手的有酒喝\NA man working outdoors feels more like a man...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.60,0:37:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才有尊严  这是我的浅见\Nif he can have a bottle of suds. That's only my opinion...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.50,0:37:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长官\Nsir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.44,0:37:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看什么看\NWhat are you jimmies staring at?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.57,0:37:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干活\NLet's go! Work!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.69,0:37:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是呢\NAnd that's how it came to pass...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:26.82,0:37:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在完工前一天\Nthat on the second-to-last day of the job...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.69,0:37:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,49年春的公差犯人\Nthe convict crew that tarred the factory roof in the spring of '49...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.46,0:37:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上十点坐成排\Nwound up sitting in a row at 10:00 in the morning...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.80,0:37:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喝着冰镇啤酒\Ndrinking icy-cold beer, courtesy of the hardest screw...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.47,0:37:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肖申克监狱历来最狠的狱官请的客\Nthat ever walked a turn at Shawshank State Prison.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:46.94,0:37:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娘儿们  趁凉快喝\NDrink up while it's cold, ladies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.48,0:37:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这王八蛋还装大方呢\NThe colossal prick even managed to sound magnanimous.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.18,0:38:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阳光洒肩头  仿佛自由人\NWe sat and drank with the sun on our shoulders and felt like free men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:01.02,0:38:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像在修缮自家屋顶\NWe could have been tarring the roof of one of our own houses.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.66,0:38:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像是造物主般自在\NWe were the lords of all creation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.06,0:38:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪呢……\NAs for Andy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.90,0:38:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他窝在凉荫下\Nhe spent that break hunkered in the shade...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.73,0:38:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,脸上挂着奇异微笑\Na strange little smile on his face...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.47,0:38:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看着我们喝他的酒\Nwatching us drink his beer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.08,0:38:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来一瓶吧？\NWant a cold one?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.82,0:38:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢  我戒酒了\NNo, thanks. I gave up drinking.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.72,0:38:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以说  他想拍狱方马屁\NYou could argue he done it to curry favor with the guards.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.49,0:38:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或是想博取狱友交情\NOr maybe make a few friends among us cons.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.03,0:38:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我呢？\NMe?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:44.30,0:38:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为他只想重温自由\NI think he did it just to feel normal again...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:47.54,0:38:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪怕只有一刹那\Nif only for a short while.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.41,0:38:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将军\NIKing me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.38,0:38:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-下棋  是帝王游戏  -什么？\N-Chess. Now there's a game of kings. -What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.21,0:38:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讲文明  重谋略\NCivilized. Strategic.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:00.61,0:39:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神秘得要死  真讨厌\NAnd a total fucking mystery. I hate it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.88,0:39:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改天我教你吧\NLet me teach you someday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:07.19,0:39:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好\NSure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.66,0:39:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想买个棋盘\NWe could get a board together.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.62,0:39:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你找对人了  我不论什么都弄得到\NYou're talking to the right man. I can get things, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.89,0:39:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,棋盘用买的  但棋子我来刻\NWe might do business on a board, and I'll carve the pieces myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.10,0:39:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一半用雪花石膏  一半用皂石\NOne side in alabaster, one in soapstone. What do you think?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.00,0:39:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要刻上许多年\NI think it'll take years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:23.60,0:39:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间有的是  就是缺石头\NYears I got. What I don't have are the rocks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.34,0:39:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,操场很贫瘠\NPickings are pretty slim in the yard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:28.51,0:39:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多半是石子\NPebbles, mostly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.68,0:39:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们算是朋友吧？\NWe're getting to be kind of friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.35,0:39:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算是吧\NYeah, I guess.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.55,0:39:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能问你个问题吗\NCan I ask you something?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.56,0:39:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你为什么杀人？\NWhy'd you do it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.23,0:39:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是清白的  瑞德\NI'm innocent, Red.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.00,0:39:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟大家一样\NJust like everybody else here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.37,0:39:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你呢？\NWhat are you in for?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.64,0:40:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟你一样  杀人\NMurder. Same as you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.01,0:40:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,清白的？\NInnocent?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:04.88,0:40:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是肖申克唯一有罪的\NOnly guilty man in Shawshank.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.71,0:41:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歌女呢？\NWhere's the canary?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.31,0:41:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么知道？\NHow did you know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:09.81,0:41:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我知道什么？  -原来你不知道\N-How did I know what?  -So you don't know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:12.31,0:41:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来\NCome.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:15.98,0:41:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歌女在这里\NThis is where the canary is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.75,0:41:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到她来寒舍献唱吧\NQuite a surprise to hear a woman singing in my house, eh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:27.60,0:41:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确……\NThat's quite a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:29.93,0:41:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到\Nsurprise.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.00,0:41:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德\NRed
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.90,0:41:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下\NWait, wait.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:37.84,0:41:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她要上场了\NHere she comes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.61,0:41:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最迷她甩头发的骚样\NI like this part when she does that shit with her hair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:42.68,0:41:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个月看过三场了\NI know. I've seen it three times this month.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.61,0:41:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姬旦  你衣着整齐吗？\NGilda, are you decent?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.52,0:41:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在说我？\NMe?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.35,0:41:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我爱死这段了\NGod, I love it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.29,0:42:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说阁下有求必应\NI understand you're a man that knows how to get things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:03.30,0:42:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下确非浪得虚名  你要什么？\NI'm known to locate certain things from time to time. What do you want?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.23,0:42:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-丽塔·海华丝  -什么？\N-Rita Hayworth. -What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.94,0:42:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弄得到吗？\NCan you get her?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.71,0:42:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位就是约翰尼·法雷尔啊  久仰久仰\NSo this is Johnny Farrel. I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.31,0:42:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-要几个星期  -几星期？\N-Take a few weeks. -Weeks?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:19.81,0:42:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又没把她压在下面  抱歉这么说\NI don't have her stuffed down the front of my pants right now, sorry to say.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.40,0:42:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沉住气哦  法雷尔先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:25.13,0:42:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正弄得到\NBut I'll get her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:26.32,0:42:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心\NRelax.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.52,0:42:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢了\NThanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:31.66,0:42:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确  你该见见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:34.40,0:42:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说了我来做什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.43,0:42:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不  我要让他惊喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.21,0:42:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-出去  -我得放映\N-Get out!  -I got to change reels!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.41,0:42:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫你滚\NI said fuck off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.56,0:43:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不尖叫吗？\NAin't you going to scream?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.26,0:43:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们算算总帐\NLet's get this over with.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.23,0:43:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他打破我鼻子\NHe broke my fucking nose!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.54,0:43:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在\NNow...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.24,0:43:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要解拉链\NI'm going to open my fly...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.68,0:43:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫你含什么你就含\Nand you'll swallow what I give you to swallow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.58,0:43:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先舔我  再舔公鸡  因为你害他流鼻血\NThen you'll swallow Rooster's.  You broke his nose.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.39,0:43:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他应该得到偿还\NHe ought to have something to show for it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.72,0:43:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它进我的嘴  就跟你分家\NYou put it in my mouth, you lose it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.79,0:43:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不  你没搞懂\NNo, you don't understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.73,0:43:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会用钻子刺穿你耳朵\NDo that and I'll put all eight inches of this in your ear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.96,0:43:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你知道吗  脑部遇袭\NAll right, but you should know that sudden, serious brain injury...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.63,0:43:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会使人死劲咬\Ncauses the victim to bite down hard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:49.77,0:43:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用力之大\NIn fact, I hear the bite reflex is so strong...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.07,0:43:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得用撬棍\Nthey have to pry the victim's jaws open...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.74,0:43:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才扳得开\Nwith a crowbar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.08,0:44:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么知道？\NWhere do you get this shit?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:02.82,0:44:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,书上写的\NI read it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.62,0:44:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你识字吗  豆腐脑？\NYou know how to read, you ignorant fuck?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:09.96,0:44:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亲爱的\NHoney!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.99,0:44:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不该损我\NYou shouldn't!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.40,0:44:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伯格斯没逼他吹喇叭\NBogs didn't put anything in Andy's mouth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.57,0:44:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其他两个也不敢\NAnd neither did his friends.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.07,0:44:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们把安迪打个半死\NWhat they did do is beat him within an inch of his life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.57,0:44:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在医务室里待了一个月\NAndy spent a month in the infirmary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:30.88,0:44:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伯格斯被关禁闭一周\NBogs spent a week in the hole.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:37.48,0:44:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间到\NTime's up, Bogs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.82,0:44:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命  头儿\NIt's your world, boss.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.76,0:44:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回牢房准备点名\NReturn to your cellblocks for evening count.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:50.76,0:44:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部回牢房\NAll prisoners report for lock down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.35,0:45:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？\NWhat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:22.03,0:45:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-他想去哪儿？  -抓住脚\N-Where's he going?  -Grab his ankles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:26.23,0:45:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要……救命！\NNo...help!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:35.31,0:45:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,此后  有两件事再也没发生过\NTwo things never happened again after that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:38.18,0:45:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三姐妹再也没碰安迪\NThe Sisters never laid a finger on Andy again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.15,0:45:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伯格斯再也无法走路\NAnd Bogs would never walk again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:45.82,0:45:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他被转送到低戒护的医院\NThey transferred him to a minimum-security hospital upstate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:49.52,0:45:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只知道他的余生\NTo my knowledge, he lived out the rest of his days...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:52.49,0:45:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠吸管进食\Ndrinking his food through a straw.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:55.33,0:45:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想热烈欢迎安迪出院\NAndy could use a nice welcome back when he gets out of the infirmary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:01.17,0:46:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题\NSounds good to us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:03.00,0:46:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们欠他的酒\NI figure we owe him that much for the beer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.24,0:46:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他喜欢下棋\NThe man likes to play chess.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:09.01,0:46:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮他找石头吧\NLet's get him some rocks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:43.54,0:46:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位！\NGuys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.55,0:46:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我找到一块\NI got one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.81,0:46:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快瞧！\NI got one. Look!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:50.22,0:46:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是皂石 也不是雪花石\NHeywood, that isn't soapstone! And it ain't alabaster either.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.49,0:46:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你他妈是地质学家？\NWhat are you, a fucking geologist?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:56.59,0:46:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说的没错\NHe's right. It ain't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.53,0:47:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-那这是什么？  -马粪蛋\N-What the hell is it then? -It's a horse apple.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:02.40,0:47:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-胡说!  -没有  就是马粪\N-Bullshit!  -No, horseshit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:05.00,0:47:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马粪化石\NPetrified.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.97,0:47:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天哪\NGod!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:15.48,0:47:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他妈的\NDamn!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:16.98,0:47:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,错误难免  但众志成城\NDespite a few hitches, the boys came through in fine style.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:21.42,0:47:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在安迪出院前一周\NAnd by the weekend he was due back...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:23.62,0:47:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石头多得够他刻一辈子\Nwe had enough rocks saved up to keep him busy till rapture.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:28.16,0:47:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同时到了一大批货\NAlso got a big shipment in that week.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:30.92,0:47:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烟\NCigarettes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:32.26,0:47:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,口香糖\Nchewing gum...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.49,0:47:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,威士忌\Nsipping whisky...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:35.16,0:47:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裸女扑克牌\Nplaying cards with naked ladies on them. You name it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.90,0:47:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然  最重要的当属\NAnd of course, the most important item:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:43.37,0:47:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,丽塔·海华丝\NRita Hayworth herself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:19.61,0:48:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,醒醒\NWake up
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.54,0:48:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心  来搜查了\NHeads up. They're tossing cells.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:25.01,0:48:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心  来搜查了\NHeads up. They're tossing cells!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.32,0:48:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,119\N119.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.65,0:48:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,123\N123.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:44.60,0:48:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站起来\NOn your feet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:48.24,0:48:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面对墙\NFace the wall.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:23.87,0:49:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,转身面向典狱长\NTurn around and face the warden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.38,0:49:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很高兴你在看圣经\NPleased to see you reading this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:35.78,0:49:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你最喜欢哪一章节？\NAny favorite passages?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:38.59,0:49:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“所以你们要惊醒，”\N"Watch ye, therefore,for ye know not...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:41.15,0:49:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“因为不知道家主何时到来。”\Nwhen the master of the house cometh."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:44.52,0:49:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马可福音  13章35节\NMark 13:35.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:47.43,0:49:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也一向喜欢它\NI've always liked that one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:50.23,0:49:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我更偏爱——\NBut I prefer...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:52.37,0:49:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“我是世界的光，”\N"I am the light of the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:54.70,0:49:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“跟从我的，就不会走进黑暗，必要得跟着生命的光。”\NYe that followeth me shall have the light of life."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:58.21,0:50:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,约翰福音  8章12节\NJohn, chapter 8, verse 12.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:01.11,0:50:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说你精通数字\NI hear you're good with numbers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:03.34,0:50:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好\NHow nice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:05.58,0:50:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人应该有专长\NMan should have a skill.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:10.05,0:50:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？\NExplain this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:12.25,0:50:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,磨石毡  打磨石头用的\NIt's called a rock blanket. It's for shaping and polishing rocks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.76,0:50:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的小嗜好\NA little hobby of mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.54,0:50:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很标准\NIt's pretty clean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:31.24,0:50:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无重大违规\NSome contraband here, but nothing to get in a twist over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:38.68,0:50:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛  我不大赞成\NI can't say I approve of this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:42.32,0:50:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过嘛……\NBut I suppose...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:45.85,0:50:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,破个例也无妨\Nexceptions can be made.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:58.23,0:50:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,锁门\NLock them up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:02.47,0:51:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差点忘了\NI almost forgot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:04.47,0:51:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怎能拿你的圣经\NI'd hate to deprive you of this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.37,0:51:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“救赎之道，就在其中。”\NSalvation lies within.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.51,0:51:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:19.12,0:51:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搜查只是借口\NTossing cells was just an excuse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:22.16,0:51:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事实是……\NTruth is...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:23.59,0:51:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诺顿要秤他斤两\NNorton wanted to size Andy up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:39.74,0:51:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我太太在教堂织的\NMy wife made that in church group.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.74,0:51:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相当精巧\NVery nice, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.61,0:51:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喜欢洗衣房的工作吗？\NYou enjoy working the laundry?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:50.75,0:51:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不怎么喜欢\NNo, sir. Not especially.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:52.79,0:51:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许我们可以换个别的……\NPerhaps we can find something more...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:55.49,0:51:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你发挥才学\Nbefitting a man of your education.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:06.00,0:52:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杰克  老布人呢？\NHey, Jake. Where's Brooks?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:08.27,0:52:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪  我听见你来了\NI thought I heard you out here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.77,0:52:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我转派给你\NI've been reassigned to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:14.61,0:52:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我听说了\NI know, they told me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:17.78,0:52:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想不到\NAin't that a kick in the head?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:20.05,0:52:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来个小小巡礼吧\NWell, I'll give you the dime tour.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:22.55,0:52:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:25.12,0:52:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都在你眼前了\NWell, here she is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:27.05,0:52:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肖申克监狱图书馆\NThe Shawshank Prison Library.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:29.72,0:52:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国家地理杂志\NNational Geographics...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.63,0:52:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,读者文摘\NReader's Digest condensed books...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:35.63,0:52:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畅销西部小说\Nand Louis L'Amour.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:37.80,0:52:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,展望杂志\NLook magazine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:39.97,0:52:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悬疑小说\NErle Stanley Gardners.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:42.57,0:52:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每晚搬上车兜一圈\NEvery evening I load up the cart and make my rounds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:46.24,0:52:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,记下借书人名字\NI enter the names on this clipboard here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:49.41,0:52:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如此往复  简简单单\NEasy, peasy, Japanese-y.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:52.41,0:52:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-有问题吗？  -你管图书馆多久了?\N-Any questions?  -How long have you been librarian?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:56.98,0:53:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1905年入狱  1912年入馆\NI come here in '05, and they made me librarian in 1912.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:02.32,0:53:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么多年都没有助手？\NAnd have you ever had an assistant?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:04.76,0:53:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有  根本用不着\NNo. Not much to it, really.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:07.93,0:53:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那为何派我来？\NWhy me? Why now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:09.60,0:53:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.10,0:53:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但有人作伴真好\NBut it'd be nice to have some company down here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:14.63,0:53:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦\NDufresne
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.38,0:53:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是他\NThat's him. That's the one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:35.32,0:53:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是狄金斯\NI'm Dekins.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:36.89,0:53:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在想……\NI was thinking...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:39.19,0:53:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为孩子弄个教育基金\Nabout setting up some kind of trust fund for my kids' educations.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:46.97,0:53:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了\NI see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:53.54,0:53:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们坐下谈吧\NWhy don't we have a seat and talk it over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:59.21,0:54:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老布  有纸笔吗？\NDo you have a piece of paper and a pencil?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:14.03,0:54:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:16.00,0:54:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么\NSo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:18.83,0:54:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狄金斯先生\NMister Dekins...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:21.40,0:54:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后安迪说\NAnd then Andy says, "Mr. Dekins...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:23.70,0:54:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“你想让贵公子进哈佛还是耶鲁？”\Ndo you want your sons to go to Harvard or Yale?"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:26.91,0:54:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你少瞎扯\NHe didn't say that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:28.31,0:54:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的  老天为证\NAs God as my witness!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:31.08,0:54:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他愣了一下\NDekins blinked for a second...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.01,0:54:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傻笑出来  后来真跟安迪握手了\Nthen he laughed and actually shook Andy's hand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:36.58,0:54:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-握你的鸟  -真的握手\N-My ass!  -Shook his hand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.09,0:54:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我乐的差点尿出来\NI tell you, I near soiled myself!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:42.19,0:54:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若给安迪弄一套西装领带\NAll he needed was a suit and tie and a jiggly hula gal on his desk...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:46.66,0:54:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他就成了“咨询先生”\Nhe'd have been "Mr. Dufresne," if you please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.46,0:54:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始交新朋友了  安迪？\NMaking a few friends?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.40,0:54:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不算“朋友”\NI wouldn't say "friends."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:54.27,0:54:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是精通理财的囚徒\NI'm a convicted murderer who provides sound financial planning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:58.30,0:55:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种本事很受用\NIt's a wonderful pet to have.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:00.84,0:55:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起码不用干洗衣工\NGot you out of the laundry, though.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.18,0:55:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还派得上更大用场\NIt might do more than that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:05.31,0:55:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比如扩建图书馆  买新书\NHow about expanding the library. Get some new books.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:08.21,0:55:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不如申请张台球桌\NIf you ask for something, ask for a pool table.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:11.38,0:55:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对\Nyes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:12.55,0:55:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想怎么弄？\NHow do you expect to do that? I mean...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:15.72,0:55:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是说  “咨询先生”  你打算怎么弄到新书？\Nget new books in here, "Mr. Dufresne, if you please."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:19.16,0:55:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找典狱长要钱\NI'll ask the warden for funds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:22.10,0:55:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孩子  我经历了六任典狱长\NSon, son, son... Six wardens have been through here in my tenure, and I've learned...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:26.60,0:55:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学到的互古不变的真理就是\None immutable, universal truth:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:29.14,0:55:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给钱是不可能的\NNot one born whose asshole...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:30.74,0:55:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们没一个生来有屁眼\Nwouldn't pucker up tighter than a snare drum when you ask for funds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:36.54,0:55:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-预算太少了  -我了解\N-The budget's stretched thin as it is.  -I see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:39.65,0:55:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以写信跟州议会要钱\NMaybe I could write the state senate and request funds from them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:43.28,0:55:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,监狱领到款只能做三种用途\NThey have only three ways to spend the taxpayers' money for prisons:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:47.59,0:55:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,筑高墙  加牢笼  添警卫\NMore walls, more bars, more guards.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:50.22,0:55:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我仍请您恩准  一周一信\NI'd like to try, with permission. A letter a week.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:53.09,0:55:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-总会有结果  -难说哦\N-They can't ignore me forever.  -Sure can.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:56.10,0:55:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想写就写吧\NBut you write your letters if it makes you happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:59.07,0:56:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定寄出  行吗？\NI'll even mail them for you. How's that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.34,0:56:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪开始一周一信\NSo Andy started writing a letter a week...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:06.34,0:56:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说话算话\Njust like he said.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:12.11,0:56:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过  就像诺顿说的\NAnd like Norton said...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:14.95,0:56:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫无回音\NAndy got no answers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:24.62,0:56:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,次年  他替半数的警卫报税\NThe following April, he did tax returns for half the guards at Shawshank.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:30.86,0:56:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再过一年  全都找他帮忙\NYear after that, he did them all...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.37,0:56:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包括典狱长的\Nincluding the warden's.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:37.04,0:56:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再过一年  狱际棒球赛\NYear after that, they rescheduled the intramural season...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:40.71,0:56:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改在与税季重叠\Nto coincide with tax season.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:44.71,0:56:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各监狱的警卫都带税单找他\NThe guards on the opposing teams all remembered to bring their W-2s.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:49.38,0:56:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狱方发枪给你\NSo Moresby Prison...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:50.92,0:56:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但要你付钱\Nissued you a gun, but you paid for it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:53.42,0:56:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连枪套也要我付\NRight. The holster too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:55.32,0:56:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这笔钱可以扣除\NThat's tax-deductible. You can write that off.
