Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:46.54,0:57:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,错在他们\NIt's what they done!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:48.71,0:57:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我别无选择\NI got no choice.
