Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:52.95,0:57:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-对  是吧赫伍？  -没错\N-Right, Heywood?  -Sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:55.65,0:57:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他是朋友  而你明理\NHe's a friend of yours, and Brooks is a reasonable man.
