Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:14.30,0:58:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有闯祸……\NIt's the only way...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:15.97,0:58:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才能留在牢里\Nthey'd let me stay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.30,0:58:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能  别做傻事\NThis is crazy. You don't want to do this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.91,0:58:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把刀放下\NPut it, put it down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:31.75,0:58:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放松点\NTake it easy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:33.92,0:58:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会有事的\NYou'll be all right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:35.66,0:58:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他没事  我呢？\NHim? What about me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.32,0:58:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老疯狗差点割断我喉咙\NCrazy old fool damn near cut my throat!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:40.93,0:58:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你刮胡子不也刀刀见血\NYou've had worse from shaving.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:43.03,0:58:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么惹毛他的？\NWhat did you do to set him off?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:45.33,0:58:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪有  我只是来道别\NNothing. I come in here to say farewell.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:48.17,0:58:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上面准他假释了\NAin't you heard? His parole's come through.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:53.04,0:58:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我实在搞不明白\NI just don't understand what happened in there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:56.18,0:58:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这老家伙简直疯了\NOld man's crazy as a rat in a tin shithouse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:59.18,0:59:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赫伍  住口\NThat's enough out of you.
