Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:04.28,0:59:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别斗嘴了\NKnock it off.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:06.45,0:59:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老布没疯\NBrooks ain't no bug.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:08.32,0:59:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他只是……\Nhe is just...
