Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:14.86,0:59:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“体制化”？  什么鸟词儿\N"Institutionalized," my ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:17.00,0:59:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他坐了50年的牢  赫伍  50年呀\NThe man's been in here 50 years, Heywood, 50 years!
