Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:25.64,0:59:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在狱中有地位\Nan educated man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:27.54,0:59:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出狱就成了废人\NOutside, he's nothing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:30.34,0:59:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,双手犯关节炎的囚徒\NJust a used-up con with arthritis in both hands.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:34.05,0:59:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想向图书馆借书都会被拒\NProbably couldn't get a library card if he tried.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.32,0:59:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样说你懂吗？\NYou know what I'm trying to say?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:39.32,0:59:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不懂你的满嘴屁话\NI do believe you're talking out of your ass.
