Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:46.33,0:59:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,监狱是怪地方\NBut I tell you these walls are funny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:50.33,0:59:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起先你恨它\NFirst you hate them.
