Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.67,0:59:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更久后\NEnough time passes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:00.34,1:00:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你离不开它\Nyou get so you depend on them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:03.34,1:00:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就叫“体制化”\NThat's "institutionalized."
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:05.75,1:00:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狗屎\NShit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:07.25,1:00:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我才不会呢  -是吗？\N-I could never get like that. -Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:10.88,1:00:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等你呆到老布那把年纪 你就知道了\NWait till you've been here as long as Brooks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:13.62,1:00:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的太对了\NGoddamn right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:17.76,1:00:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们把你送到这里来度日\NThey send you here for life...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:20.36,1:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等于拿走你一生的年华\Nthat's exactly what they take.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.43,1:00:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少是一大部分\NPart that counts, anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:34.04,1:00:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杰克  我无法再照顾你\NI can't take care of you no more, Jake.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:38.14,1:00:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧  你自由了\NYou go on now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.05,1:00:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自由了\NYou're free.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:43.82,1:00:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自由了\NYou're free.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:04.40,1:01:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切顺利  老布\NGood luck, Brooksie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:08.37,1:01:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.04,1:01:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“亲爱的牢友：”\NDear fellas:
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:45.81,1:01:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“外头的变化快得难以置信。”\NI can't believe how fast things move on the outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:51.32,1:01:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老头儿  嫌命长吗\NWatch it, old-timer! Want to get killed?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:55.22,1:01:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“小时候我只看过一辆汽车，”\NI saw an automobile once when I was a kid...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:59.36,1:02:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“如今满街都是，”\Nbut now they're everywhere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.47,1:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“整个世界忙成一团。”\NThe world went and got itself in a big damn hurry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:25.59,1:02:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“上面安排我”\NThe parole board got me into this halfway house...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:29.66,1:02:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“到‘中途之家’，”\Ncalled "The Brewer"...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:31.52,1:02:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“并在超市”\Nand a job...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.89,1:02:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“当包装员。”\Nbagging groceries at the Food-Way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:37.40,1:02:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“工作辛苦，我也卖力，”\NIt's hard work and I try to keep up...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:40.03,1:02:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“但双手一直犯疼。”\N..but my hands hurt most of the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:42.70,1:02:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫他务必用双层袋\NMake sure your man double-bags.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.87,1:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上次差点撑破袋子\NLast time, the bottom near came out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:47.57,1:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确定要用双层袋\NMake sure you double-bag like the lady says. understand?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:50.71,1:02:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是  没问题\NYes, sir. Surely will.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:52.28,1:02:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“店长不怎么喜欢我。”\NI don't think the store manager likes me very much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.82,1:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“工作之余我去公园喂鸟，”\NSometimes after work, I go to the park and feed the birds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:03.56,1:03:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“盼望……”\NI keep thinking...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.29,1:03:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“杰克来打个招呼，”\NJake might just show up and say hello.
