Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.43,1:03:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“不管它在何处，我祝它过的好、有新朋友。”\NI hope, wherever he is, he's doing okay and making new friends.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:20.91,1:03:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“我夜间难以入眠，”\NI have trouble sleeping at night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:23.94,1:03:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“做着从高处坠落的噩梦。”\NI have bad dreams like I'm falling.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:27.48,1:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“从梦中惊醒，”\NI wake up scared.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:29.92,1:03:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“有时记不起身在何方。”\NSometimes it takes me a while to remember where I am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:35.66,1:03:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“也许我该持枪抢劫，好让他们送我回去。”\NMaybe I should get a gun and rob the Food-Way so they'd send me home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:40.86,1:03:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“我可以打死那个店长，当作额外奖励。”\NI could shoot the manager while I was at it. Sort of like a bonus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:46.87,1:03:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“但我老的无法再胡闹了。”\NI guess I'm too old for that sort of nonsense anymore.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:51.10,1:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“我不喜欢这里，”\NI don't like it here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.04,1:03:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“我厌倦成天担惊受怕。”\NI'm tired of being afraid all the time. I've decided...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:57.88,1:03:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“于是，我决心不再逗留。”\Nnot to stay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:10.46,1:04:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“当局不会在乎我，”\NI doubt they'll kick up any fuss...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.23,1:04:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“一个糟老头算什么。”\Nnot for an old crook like me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:19.19,1:05:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“当局不会在乎我，一个糟老头算什么。”\N"I doubt they'll kick up any fuss, not for an old crook like me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:24.50,1:05:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“还有，替我向赫伍道歉，”\NP.S. Tell Heywood I'm sorry I put a knife to his throat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:28.53,1:05:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“别记恨在心。你们的老布”\NNo hard feelings. Brooks."
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:41.35,1:05:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他还不如老死在肖申克好\NHe should have died in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:48.85,1:05:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞧瞧你干的好事\NWhat the fuck have you done?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:50.46,1:05:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一片混乱\NIt's a goddamn mess, I'll tell you that.
