Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:47.11,1:06:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干的好  安迪\NGood for you, Andy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:51.25,1:06:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇！\NWow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:53.59,1:06:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只写了六年\NIt only took six years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:57.09,1:06:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在起我一周两封\NFrom now on, I'll write two letters a week instead of one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:00.03,1:07:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真够固执的  听队长的话\NI believe you're crazy enough.  Get this stuff out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.63,1:07:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把东西清干净  我去解大便\Nlike he said. I've got to pinch a loaf.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:06.27,1:07:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别让我出来\NWhen I come back...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:07.93,1:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再看到这些\Nthis is all gone, all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:58.45,1:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪  什么声音？\NDo you hear that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:08.59,1:09:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦\NDufresne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.29,1:09:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪  放我出去！\NAndy, let me out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:16.80,1:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪！\NAndy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:20.70,1:09:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到现在我还搞不懂她们唱什么\NI have no idea to this day what those two Italian ladies were singing about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:25.94,1:09:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实我也不想弄懂\NTruth is, I don't want to know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:28.37,1:09:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,此时无言胜有言\NSome things are best left unsaid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:34.45,1:09:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她们唱出\NI like to think it was something so beautiful...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:37.38,1:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难以言传的美\Nit can't be expressed in words...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:39.72,1:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美得令你心碎\Nand makes your heart ache because of it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:44.29,1:09:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歌声直窜云端\NI tell you, those voices soared...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:47.06,1:09:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超越失意囚徒的梦想\Nhigher and farther than anybody in a gray place dares to dream.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:51.56,1:09:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宛如小鸟飞入牢房\NIt was like a beautiful bird flapped into our drab cage...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:55.13,1:09:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使石墙消失无踪\Nand made those walls dissolve away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:58.34,1:10:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在这一瞬间\NAnd for the briefest of moments...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:00.74,1:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肖申克众囚仿佛重获自由\Nevery last man at Shawshank felt free.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:06.31,1:10:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,典狱长可发飚了\NIt pissed the warden off something awful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:10.28,1:10:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开门\NOpen the door.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:14.19,1:10:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开门\NOpen it up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:17.26,1:10:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦  开门\NDufresne, open this door!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:21.33,1:10:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关掉\NTurn that off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:29.60,1:10:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我警告你  关掉\NI am warning you. Turn that off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:46.15,1:10:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦\NDufresne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:49.79,1:10:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敬酒不吃吃罚酒\NYou're mine now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.76,1:11:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪被关禁闭两周\NAndy got two weeks in the hole for that little stunt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:02.20,1:11:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站起来\NOn your feet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.97,1:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-看谁来了  -大指挥家\N-Hey, look who's here.  -Maestro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.14,1:11:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没别的可放吗？  比如汉克·威廉斯的歌？\NYou couldn't play something good, huh? Like Hank Williams?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:13.15,1:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没等接受点歌  他们就破门而入了\NThey broke the door down before I could take requests.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:16.15,1:11:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-关两周值得吗？  -我最舒服的两周\N-Was it worth two weeks?  -Easiest time I ever did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:19.49,1:11:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-屁话  关小号最难熬了  -在里面度日如年\N-No such thing as easy time in the hole. -A week in the hole is like a year.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:23.89,1:11:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-半点不假  -有莫札特陪我\N-Damn straight.  -I had Mr. Mozart to keep me company.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:27.39,1:11:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们准你带留声机？\NSo they let you tote that record player down there, huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:32.80,1:11:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在脑中\NIt was in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:35.00,1:11:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在心底\NIn here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:37.37,1:11:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,音乐之美\NThat's the beauty of music.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:39.67,1:11:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是夺不走的\NThey can't get that from you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:45.54,1:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没体会过吗？\NHaven't you ever felt that way about music?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:49.72,1:11:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我年轻时吹过口琴\NWell, I played a mean harmonica as a younger man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:53.89,1:11:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来没兴致了\NLost interest in it, though.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:55.79,1:11:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在牢里也没意义\NDidn't make much sense in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.72,1:11:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是在这里才有意义\NHere's where it makes the most sense.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:00.26,1:12:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有音乐才不会忘记\NYou need it so you don't forget.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:02.90,1:12:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忘记什么？\NForget?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:04.46,1:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世上\NForget that there are...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.77,1:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有些地方\Nplaces...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:09.70,1:12:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是石墙围不住的\Nin the world that aren't made out of stone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:14.54,1:12:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在人的\NThere's something...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:16.38,1:12:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,内心深处\Ninside...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.04,1:12:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有他们找不到\Nthat they can't get to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.21,1:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿不走的东西\Nthat they can't touch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:22.11,1:12:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全属于你自己的东西\NThat's yours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:25.08,1:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你指什么？\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:27.72,1:12:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望\NHope.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:30.02,1:12:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望\NHope.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:33.29,1:12:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朋友  我告诉你\NLet me tell you something, my friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.10,1:12:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有希望才危险\NHope is a dangerous thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:39.57,1:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望能把人逼疯\NHope can drive a man insane.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:42.63,1:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这里  希望毫无用处\NIt's got no use on the inside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:44.97,1:12:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你最好认命\NYou'd better get used to that idea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:49.68,1:12:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要像老布一样吗？\NLike Brooks did?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:16.54,1:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坐下\NSit down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.88,1:13:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据你的材料 你的终身监禁已经服满30年\NSays here that you've served 30 years of a life sentence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:27.35,1:13:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你改过自新了吗？\NYou feel you've been rehabilitated?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:29.62,1:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的\NOh, yes, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:32.12,1:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的已经变好了\NWithout a doubt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:34.62,1:13:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我完全洗心革面了\NI can honestly say I'm a changed man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:39.02,1:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会再危害社会\NNo danger to society here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:41.49,1:13:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我向上帝发誓\NGod's honest truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:45.60,1:13:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我绝对改过自新了\NAbsolutely rehabilitated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:57.74,1:13:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,30年了\NThirty years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:01.05,1:14:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老天  真不知该说什么？\NJesus, when you say it like that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:03.82,1:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些日子怎么熬过来的\NYou wonder where it went.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.05,1:14:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我连前十年都不记得了\NI wonder where 10 years went.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:15.19,1:14:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿去\NHere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:16.66,1:14:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,假释被拒的礼物\NA little parole rejection present.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:20.67,1:14:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打开看看\NGo ahead and open it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:23.47,1:14:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别介意我找你同行买\NWent through one of your competitors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:25.70,1:14:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只想给你一个惊喜\NI hope you don't mind. I wanted it to be a surprise.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:38.88,1:14:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂亮极了\NIt's very pretty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:42.09,1:14:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:45.86,1:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不吹吗？\NYou going to play it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:51.90,1:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不\NNo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:56.77,1:14:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是时候\NNot right now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:15.85,1:15:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进牢\NRoll in!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:53.16,1:15:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熄灯\NLights out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:28.99,1:16:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪言出必行\NAndy was as good as his word.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:31.50,1:16:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每周写两封信\NHe wrote two letters a week instead of one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:36.34,1:16:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,59年  州议会终于明白\NIn 1959, the state senate finally clued in to the fact...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:40.67,1:16:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两百元无法打发安迪\Nthey couldn't buy him off with just a $ 200 check.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:44.01,1:16:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当局决定每年拨款五百美元\NAppropriations Committee voted an annual payment of $500...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:48.51,1:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好让安迪封笔\Njust to shut him up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:50.62,1:16:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想像不到他的能耐\NAnd you'd be amazed how far Andy could stretch it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:53.82,1:16:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他接洽读书会  慈善团体\NHe made deals with book clubs, charity groups.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:56.96,1:16:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他论斤买入旧书\NHe bought remaindered books by the pound...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:00.23,1:17:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,《金银岛》\N"Treasure Island".
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:02.29,1:17:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,罗伯特·路易斯\NRobert Louis...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:03.83,1:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,史蒂文森\NStevenson.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:05.06,1:17:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冒险小说类\NFiction, adventure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:09.00,1:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一本\NWhat's next?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:10.24,1:17:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汽车维修\NI got here Auto Repair...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:14.04,1:17:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肥皂雕刻\Nand Soap Carving.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:15.41,1:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,专业技术及嗜好  教育类  在你后面\NTrade skills and hobbies. Under "Educational," behind you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:18.84,1:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基堵山恩仇记\NCount of Monte Crisco.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:21.18,1:17:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基督山  饭桶\NThat's "Cristo," you dumb shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:24.58,1:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作者亚历山大……\NBy Alexandree...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:26.05,1:17:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大种马\NDum-ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:27.65,1:17:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,种马？\NDumb ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:30.99,1:17:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,种马？\NDumb ass?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:34.96,1:17:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大仲马  内容知道吗？\NDumas. Know what that's about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:39.20,1:17:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讲逃狱  你会喜欢的\NYou'd like it. It's about a prison break.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:41.37,1:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那该归入教育类啰\NWe ought to file that under "Educational" too, oughtn't we?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:46.14,1:17:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大伙儿尽可能地帮忙\NThe rest of us did our best to pitch in when and where we could.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:50.81,1:17:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在肯尼迪遇刺那年\NBy the year Kennedy was shot...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:52.81,1:17:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪把这间臭储藏室变成\NAndy had transformed a storage room smelling of turpentine...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:57.62,1:18:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新英格兰最棒的监狱图书馆\Ninto the best prison library in New England...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:01.42,1:18:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚至有汉克·威廉斯精选集\Ncomplete with a fine selection of Hank Williams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:11.73,1:18:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在同年\NThat was also when Warden Norton...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:13.87,1:18:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,典狱长实施著名的“外役”专案\Ninstituted his famous "Inside Out" program.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:17.27,1:18:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许你曾在报上看过\NYou may remember reading about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:19.57,1:18:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他上了各报和《展望杂志》\NIt made the papers and got his picture in Look magazine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:22.87,1:18:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是放任自由\NIt's no free ride...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:24.38,1:18:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是狱政的\Nbut rather a genuine progressive advance...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:27.81,1:18:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一大进步\Nin corrections and rehabilitation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:30.65,1:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本监获刑人在妥善监督下\NOur inmates, properly supervised...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:33.39,1:18:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将到狱外劳动\Nwill be put to work outside these walls...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:36.22,1:18:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从事各项公共事业\Nperforming all manner of public service.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:39.49,1:18:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们将学到诚实劳动的价值\NThese men can learn the value...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:42.49,1:18:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同时为社区提供服务\Nof an honest day's labor and provide a service to the community...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:46.50,1:18:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对于纳税大众而言  也只花最少的代价\Nat a bare minimum of expense to Mr. And Mrs. John Q. Taxpayer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:51.64,1:18:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然  诺顿没向媒体说明\NOf course he didn't tell the press...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:54.17,1:18:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“最少代价”实在含糊不清\Nthat "bare minimum of expense" is a fairly loose term.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:57.84,1:19:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,揩油的方法何止百种\NThere are 100 different ways to skim off the top.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:01.08,1:19:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人力  物料  处处漏洞\NMen, materials, you name it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:03.92,1:19:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天哪  油水超多\NAnd oh, my Lord, how the money rolled in!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:07.02,1:19:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会害我倒闭的\NAt this rate, you'll put me out of business.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:09.75,1:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠这么多奴工  谁投标投得过你\NWith this pool of slave labor, you can underbid any contractor in town.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:14.76,1:19:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们在提供社区服务\NWe're providing a valuable community service.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:17.93,1:19:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是说词  我得养家\NThat's fine for the papers, but I've got a family to feed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:24.27,1:19:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老兄  咱们这么久的交情\NWe go back a long way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:27.11,1:19:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我需要包下这条公路  不然只好喝西北风了\NI need this highway contract. I don't get it and I go under. That's a fact.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:32.94,1:19:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我太太特地为你烤的派\NYou have some of this fine pie...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:34.98,1:19:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请笑纳\Nmy missus made for you. You think about that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:46.59,1:19:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别担心这项工程合约\NI wouldn't worry too much about this contract.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:49.53,1:19:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已叫他们接别的项目了\NI already got my boys committed elsewhere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:54.57,1:19:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮我谢谢她的心意\NYou be sure and thank Maisie for this fine pie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:58.74,1:20:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在每一桩买卖背后\NAnd behind every shady deal...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:01.24,1:20:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在每一个黑钱底下\Nbehind every dollar earned...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:04.14,1:20:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都有安迪在  是他做的帐\Nthere was Andy, keeping the books.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:07.61,1:20:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有两笔要存入银行\NTwo deposits.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:09.11,1:20:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照旧在夜间  存到缅因国际和新英格兰\NMaine National and New England First. Night drops as always, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:43.45,1:20:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把东西拿去洗衣房  两套西装和杂物\NGet my stuff to the laundry. Two suits for dry-clean and a bag of whatnot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:48.25,1:20:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-别浆太硬  否则有他们好看  -是  先生\NIf they over-starch my shirts again, they'll hear from me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:51.99,1:20:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怎样？\NHow do I look?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:54.36,1:20:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-很好  先生  -要去参加盛大的慈善宴会\N-Very nice.  -Big charity to-do up Portland way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:57.05,1:20:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,州长会到\NGovernor will be there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:00.00,1:21:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剩下的给你吃\NYou want the rest of this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:02.80,1:21:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烤的难吃透顶\NWoman can't bake worth shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:05.97,1:21:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢您  先生\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:10.14,1:21:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我听说这种派他收过很多\NHe's got his fingers in a lot of pies, from what I hear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:13.58,1:21:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听说的只是皮毛  他干的坏事你根本想不到  重重的回扣\NHe's got scams you haven't even dreamed of. Kickbacks on his kickbacks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:18.62,1:21:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑钱如河般在他脚下流\NA river of dirty money running through here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.19,1:21:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贪污这么多迟早会曝光\NSooner or later, he'll have to explain where it came from.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:25.22,1:21:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此才要用我\NThat's where I come in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:27.59,1:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我过滤黑钱  一一漂白\NI channel it. Filter it. Funnel it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:30.10,1:21:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,股票  证券  市政公债\NStocks, securities, tax-free municipals.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:33.26,1:21:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我让脏钱流入市场  等它回流时……\NI send it out into the real world, and when it comes back...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:37.00,1:21:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-干净的像处女？  -比那更干净\N-Clean as a virgin's honeypot, huh?  -Cleaner.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:40.57,1:21:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诺顿退休时  将是百万富翁\NBy the time Norton retires, I'll have made him a millionaire.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:46.51,1:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若被逮到  他也会被关入肖申克\NIf they ever catch on, he'll wind up in here wearing a number himself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:51.12,1:21:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你对我这么没信心啊\NI thought you had more faith in me than that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:54.02,1:21:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你很能干  但总会有蛛丝马迹留下\NI know you're good, but all that paper leaves a trail.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:57.26,1:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万一调查局或国税局起疑\NNow anybody gets curious, FBI, IRS...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:00.86,1:22:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就完了\Nwhatever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.29,1:22:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总有人要遭殃\NIt'll lead to somebody.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:03.80,1:22:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错  但不是我  更不是典狱长\NSure it is, but not to me, and certainly not to the warden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:12.04,1:22:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是谁？\NAll right, who?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:13.24,1:22:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰道·史帝文\NRandall Stevens.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:15.31,1:22:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁？\NWho?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:16.51,1:22:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隐名又隐形的合伙人\NThe "silent" silent partner.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:18.71,1:22:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,法官  要怪怪他  户头是他的\NHe's the guilty one, the man with the bank accounts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:21.98,1:22:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是洗钱的起点\NIt's where the filtering process starts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:24.35,1:22:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出了差错  只追得到他\NThey trace anything, it'll just lead to him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:27.82,1:22:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但他是什么人？\NBut who is he?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.25,1:22:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是幻影  幽灵  兔子哈维的远房表亲\NHe's a phantom, an apparition. Second cousin to Harvey the Rabbit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:34.33,1:22:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他由我一手\NI conjured him...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:35.69,1:22:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,凭空塑造\Nout of thin air.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:37.86,1:22:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他不存在  除了在文件上\NHe doesn't exist, except on paper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:43.67,1:22:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪有凭空造人的？\NYou can't just make a person up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:46.24,1:22:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,利用制度的漏洞就行\NSure you can, if you know how the system works.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:49.84,1:22:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠写信能办成太多的事\NIt's amazing what you can accomplish by mail.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:53.01,1:22:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,史帝文有出生证明\NMr. Stevens has a birth certificate...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:55.85,1:22:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有驾照  社会保险编号\Ndriver's license, Social Security.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:58.25,1:22:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在逗我吧？\NYou're shitting me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:59.45,1:23:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算抓到蛛丝马迹\NIf they trace any accounts, they'll wind up chasing...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:03.02,1:23:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也等于捕风捉影\Na figment of my imagination.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:04.96,1:23:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想不到\NWell, I'll be damned!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:08.29,1:23:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有称赞过你吧？\NDid I say you were good?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:10.40,1:23:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你简直是大艺术家\NShit, you are Rembrandt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:12.76,1:23:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可笑的是\NThe funny thing is...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:14.70,1:23:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在外头  我刚正不阿\Non the outside, I was an honest man, straight as an arrow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.20,1:23:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进了牢  却大搞欺骗\NI had to come to prison to be a crook.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:30.42,1:23:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你担心过吗？\NEver bother you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:33.15,1:23:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没干坏事  只是洗钱\NI don't run the scams. I just process the profits.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:36.49,1:23:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许这是强词夺理\NA fine line, maybe...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:39.06,1:23:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我建起图书馆\Nbut I also built that library...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:41.33,1:23:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮助囚友考取高中文凭\Nand used it to help guys get their high school diploma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:44.56,1:23:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,典狱长凭什么放任不管？\NWhy do you think he lets me do all that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:47.00,1:23:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了使你\NIKeep you happy and doing the laundry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:49.40,1:23:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乐于帮他洗钱\NMoney instead of sheets.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:51.24,1:23:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我算是便宜卖给他\NWell, I work cheap. That's the tradeoff.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:11.09,1:24:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汤米在65年来到肖申克\NTommy Williams came to Shawshank in 1965...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:13.96,1:24:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,犯了“入室行窃”  判了两年\Non a two-year stretch for B and E.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:16.43,1:24:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是强行侵入他人公宅\NThat's breaking and entering to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:19.03,1:24:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他在商店后门偷彩电时被逮\NCops caught him sneaking TV sets out the back door of a JC Penney.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:23.70,1:24:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小朋克\NYoung punk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:25.20,1:24:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,摇滚狂一个\NMr. Rock 'n' Roll...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:27.04,1:24:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跩得够可爱\Ncocky as hell.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:28.77,1:24:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点 老家伙们 慢得跟糖浆一样\NCome on, old boys. Moving like molasses!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:31.41,1:24:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看了难过\NMaking me look bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:33.38,1:24:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人见人爱\NWe liked him immediately.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:35.41,1:24:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我退出门外  就这样抱着电视\NI'm backing out the door and I got the TV like this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:39.45,1:24:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它很大  害我看不见  忽然传来\NA big old thing. I couldn't see shit. Then I hear this voice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:43.72,1:24:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“别动，举起手来！”\N"Freeze, kid, hands in the air."
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:45.89,1:24:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我站着抱紧电视\NI was standing there, holding onto that TV. Finally the voice says:
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:50.56,1:24:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他又说  “你听到没有？”  我说  “听到，但我若松手，”\N"You hear what I said, boy?" I say, "Yes, sir. I did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:54.57,1:24:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“就要添一条毁坏财产罪。”\NBut if I drop this, you get me on destruction of property too."
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:02.51,1:25:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在凯希曼监狱蹲过？\NYou done some stretch in Cashman, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:05.31,1:25:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那儿要好过得多\NYeah, that was an easy piece of time, let me tell you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:09.55,1:25:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,周末回家  活也轻松\NWeekend furloughs. Work programs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:11.68,1:25:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不像这里\NNot like here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:12.95,1:25:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你哪里都蹲过嘛\NSounds like you done time all over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:15.82,1:25:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我13岁起以牢为家\NI've been in and out since I was 13.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:18.42,1:25:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你叫得上名的监狱我都待过\NName it, chances are I've been there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:20.83,1:25:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许你该改行了\NPerhaps you should try a new profession.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:24.93,1:25:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,依我看\NWhat I mean is...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:26.83,1:25:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的贼功不灵光  该做做别的事\Nyou're not a very good thief.You should try something else.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:30.50,1:25:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你懂个屁  你是卡彭？\NYeah, what the hell you know about it, Capone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:34.14,1:25:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你因何入狱？\NWhat are you in for?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:36.01,1:25:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我？\NMe?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:39.44,1:25:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被律师害了\NA lawyer fucked me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:45.02,1:25:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肖申克没人有罪  你不知道？\NEverybody's innocent in here. Don't you know that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:55.89,1:26:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汤米有娇妻和刚出生的女儿\NAs it turned out, Tommy had himself a young wife and a new baby girl.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:00.87,1:26:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他怕妻女流落街头\NMaybe he thought of them on the streets...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:03.20,1:26:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到头来不认识老爸\Nor his child growing up not knowing her daddy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:06.00,1:26:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或是别的什么原因\NWhatever it was...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:07.71,1:26:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正这小子卯上了\Nsomething lit a fire under that boy's ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:13.98,1:26:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想考高中文凭\NThought I might try for my high school equivalency.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:17.05,1:26:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说你帮过人\NHear you helped a couple of fellas with that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:20.92,1:26:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不帮废柴\NI don't waste time with losers, Tommy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:24.56,1:26:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不是废柴\NI ain't no goddamn loser.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:28.79,1:26:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你当真？  -对\N-You mean that?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:32.30,1:26:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的当真？\NYou really mean that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:34.77,1:26:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的\NYes, sir, I do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:36.33,1:26:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好  要冲就冲到底\NGood. Because if we do this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:38.50,1:26:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百分之百努力  不可半途而废\Nwe do it all the way, a hundred percent, nothing half-assed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:42.71,1:26:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问题是……\NThing is, see...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:45.78,1:26:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不太识字\NI don't read so good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:48.48,1:26:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧\NWell.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:51.58,1:26:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不太识字……\NYou don't read...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:53.55,1:26:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系\Nso well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:57.42,1:26:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交给我吧\NWe'll get to that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:03.36,1:27:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪收汤米为徒\NSo, Andy took Tommy under his wing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:05.70,1:27:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从字母教起\NStarted walking him through his ABC's.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:10.47,1:27:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汤米学得非常好\NTommy took to it pretty well too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:12.94,1:27:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他从未发现自己有天份\NBoy found brains he never knew he had.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:18.04,1:27:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没多久就开始准备考试\NBefore long, Andy started him on his course requirements.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:21.68,1:27:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪真心喜欢他\NHe really liked the kid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:23.55,1:27:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,助人向上令他兴奋\NGave him a thrill to help a youngster crawl off the shit heap.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:27.62,1:27:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但动机不止于此\NBut that wasn't the only reason.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:30.59,1:27:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牢狱生活漫长得很\NPrison time is slow time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:33.26,1:27:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须找事打发时间\NSo you do what you can to keep going.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:36.19,1:27:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人集邮\NSome fellas collect stamps.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:38.66,1:27:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人盖火柴屋\NOthers build matchstick houses.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:41.73,1:27:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪成立了图书馆\NAndy built a library.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:44.90,1:27:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今他需要新事由\NNow he needed a new project.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:47.71,1:27:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是汤米\NTommy was it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:49.84,1:27:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这跟他长年刻石一样\NIt was the same reason he spent years shaping and polishing those rocks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:54.38,1:27:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也跟他挂美女图一样\NThe same reason he hung his fantasy girlies on the wall.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:58.52,1:27:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在牢里\NIn prison...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:00.05,1:28:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事也得找事做\Na man will do most anything to keep his mind occupied.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:04.56,1:28:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1966年  就在汤米应考之前\NBy 1966, right about the time Tommy was getting ready to take his exams...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:09.66,1:28:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,换上拉寇儿·薇芝了\Nit was lovely Raquel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:28.41,1:28:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间到\NTime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:35.45,1:28:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎样？\NWell?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:38.06,1:28:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烂透了\NWell, it's for shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:40.69,1:28:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我他妈白费一整年\NI wasted a whole year of my time with this bullshit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:43.73,1:28:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许没那么糟\NIt's probably not that bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:45.43,1:28:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就没一道题做对  简直像看中文\NI didn't get a thing right. It might as well have been in Chinese.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:49.87,1:28:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分数出来再说\NLet's see how the score comes out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:51.80,1:28:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我告诉你几分吧\NI'll tell you how the goddamn score comes out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:56.71,1:28:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两分投篮\NTwo points, right there!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:58.28,1:28:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是该死的成绩\NThere's your goddamn score!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:00.08,1:29:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么猫爬树  五五二十五\NGoddamn cats crawling up trees, 5 times 5 is 25...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:04.72,1:29:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去他妈的这鬼地方\NFuck this place!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:06.58,1:29:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去他妈的\NFuck it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:26.87,1:29:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真后悔\NI feel bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:28.34,1:29:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让他失望了\NI let him down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:29.74,1:29:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胡说\NThat's crap, kid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:31.68,1:29:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他以你为荣\NHe's proud of you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:33.34,1:29:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多年的交情  我摸透他了\NWe're old friends,I know him as good as anybody.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:36.41,1:29:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是聪明人\NSmart fellow, ain't he?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:38.18,1:29:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝顶聪明  曾是银行家\NSmart as they come. He was a banker on the outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:41.52,1:29:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他究竟为何入狱?\NWhat's he in here for anyway?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:44.06,1:29:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谋杀\NMurder.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:46.52,1:29:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你少扯了\NThe hell, you say.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:50.03,1:29:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看他外表是想不到\NYou wouldn't think it to look at the guy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:53.60,1:29:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,捉到老婆跟高尔夫球教练在床  两个全干掉了\NCaught his wife in bed with some golf pro. Greased them both.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:05.71,1:30:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？\NWhat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:08.05,1:30:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大约四年前\NAbout four years ago...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:10.88,1:30:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在托马斯顿监狱服刑\NI was in Thomaston on a two-to-three stretch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:14.62,1:30:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我偷了车\NI stole a car.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:16.29,1:30:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实在愚蠢\NIt was a dumb-fuck thing to do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:18.96,1:30:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刑期还剩半年时\NAbout six months left to go...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:21.49,1:30:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来了个新室友\NI get a new cellmate in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:24.10,1:30:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厄摩·布拉奇\NElmo Blatch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:26.43,1:30:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋一个  大个子  神经质\NBig, twitchy fucker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.63,1:30:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁都怕碰上这种室友  明白我的意思吧\NIKind of roomie you pray you don't get. You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:32.34,1:30:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,持械抢劫  服刑6至12年\NSix-to-twelve, armed burglary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:35.34,1:30:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说他干过好几百票\NSaid he pulled hundreds of jobs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:37.81,1:30:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到有那么神经的人  你放个响屁  他都能离地三尺\NHard to believe, high-strung as he was.You cut a loud fart, he jumped three feet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:43.81,1:30:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的嘴永远闭不上\NTalked all the time too. That's the other thing. He never shut up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:48.65,1:30:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他去过的地方\NPlaces he'd been in...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:50.59,1:30:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,犯过的罪行  玩过的女人\Njobs he'd pulled, women he fucked.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:53.89,1:30:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚至杀过的人\NEven people he killed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:57.33,1:31:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说杀人\NPeople who "gave him shit."
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.77,1:31:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是因为不爽\NThat's how he put it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:03.63,1:31:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有一晚  就当玩笑\NSo one night, like a joke...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:08.11,1:31:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我问他  “你杀过谁？”\NI say to him, "Elmo, who did you kill?"
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:11.84,1:31:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说——\NSo he says:
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:13.14,1:31:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在俱乐部收盘子\NI got me this job one time, busing tables at a country club...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:17.78,1:31:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁机观察阔人下手\Nso I could case all these bigrich pricks that come in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:23.79,1:31:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相中一人\NSo I pick out this guy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:26.69,1:31:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在晚上\Ngo in one night...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:28.46,1:31:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,摸进他家\Nand do his place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:31.63,1:31:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他醒来\NHe wakes up...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:33.70,1:31:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惹得我不爽\Nand gives me shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:36.53,1:31:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就杀了他\NSo I killed him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:39.97,1:31:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和他身边那骚货\NHim and this tasty bitch he was with.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:44.21,1:31:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,精彩的是\NAnd that's the best part.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:47.14,1:31:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽搞上这个高尔夫球教练\NShe's fucking this prick, see...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:49.81,1:31:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她却是个有夫之妇\Nthis golf pro, but she's married to some other guy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:53.48,1:31:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她老公  一个大银行家\NSome hotshot banker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:57.49,1:31:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成了替罪羊\NAnd he's the one they pinned it on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:11.47,1:32:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我从未听过如此惊人的故事\NI have to say that's the most amazing story I ever heard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:16.61,1:32:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最惊人的是你居然受骗\NWhat amazes me most is you'd be taken in by it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:19.84,1:32:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？\NSir?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:23.05,1:32:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,显然汤米对你颇有好感\NIt's obvious this fellow Williams is impressed with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:27.25,1:32:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道你很痛苦  自然想让你高兴\NHe hears your tale of woe and naturally wants to cheer you up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:31.39,1:32:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他还年轻  脑筋不太灵光\NHe's young, not terribly bright.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:34.09,1:32:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不明白这反而会害苦了你\NIt's not surprising he wouldn't know what a state he put you in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:37.93,1:32:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先生  他说的是实情\NSir, he's telling the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:40.26,1:32:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算真有厄摩这人\NLet's say for the moment this Blatch does exist.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:44.70,1:32:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道他会跪地哭诉  “是我杀的，我忏悔，”\NYou think he'd just fall to his knees and cry, "Yes, I did it. I confess.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:49.54,1:32:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“顺便再给我加个无期徒刑吧。”\NBy the way, add a life term to my sentence."
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:52.44,1:32:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有汤米的证词 我就可以要求重审\NWith Tommy's testimony,I can get a new trial.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:55.45,1:32:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你得找到厄摩\NThat's assuming Blatch is still there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:58.15,1:33:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他可能早就出狱了\NChances are, he'd be released by now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:00.28,1:33:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该能查到住址  这可是机会\NThey'd have his last known address.It's a chance, isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:07.22,1:33:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真是个木头\NHow can you be so obtuse?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:09.89,1:33:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:12.40,1:33:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说我什么？\NWhat did you call me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:14.07,1:33:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你笨蛋  我说错了吗？\NObtuse. Is it deliberate?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:16.17,1:33:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别忘了身份\NYou're forgetting yourself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:18.00,1:33:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俱乐部有厄摩的考勤卡\NThe country club will have his old timecards.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:21.14,1:33:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,履历  税单\NRecords, W-2s with his name on them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:24.11,1:33:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你爱幻想  那是你的事\NIf you want to indulge this fantasy, it's your business.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:27.01,1:33:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别给我添麻烦  面谈结束\NDon't make it mine. This meeting is over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:29.81,1:33:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我若出狱  绝不提你的事\NIf I got out, I'd never mention what happens here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:33.05,1:33:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为洗钱  与你同罪\NI'd be as indictable as you for laundering that money.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:37.05,1:33:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不许你提钱这个字  混账东西\NDon't ever mention money to me, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:41.03,1:33:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,办公室里不许提\NNot in this office...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:42.89,1:33:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到哪里都不许提  来人！\Nnot anywhere. Get in here, now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:45.06,1:33:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想让你放心  没别的意思\NI just wanted to put you at ease, that's all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:48.40,1:33:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小号  一个月\NSolitary. A month.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:50.67,1:33:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你是怎么搞的？  -带走\N-what's wrong with you? -Get him out of here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:53.67,1:33:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我重获自由的机会  我的人生转机  你不懂吗？\NThis is my chance to get out! It's my life! Understand?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:57.44,1:33:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,带出去\NGet him out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.28,1:34:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小号  一个月\NA month in the hole.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:03.45,1:34:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从没听过这么严厉的惩罚\NThat's the longest stretch I ever heard of.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:06.35,1:34:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是我不对\NIt's all my fault.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:07.85,1:34:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胡说八道\NBullshit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:10.12,1:34:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没杀人  也没判安迪的罪\NYou didn't pull the trigger or convict him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:13.02,1:34:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是说安迪没罪？\NAre you saying Andy is innocent?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:15.63,1:34:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真的无辜？\NI mean, for real innocent?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:17.86,1:34:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来是这样\NIt looks that way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:19.63,1:34:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的天\NSweet Jesus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:21.80,1:34:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他服刑多久了？\NHow long has he been here now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:24.03,1:34:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,47年进来  19年了\N1947. What is that? Nineteen years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:27.54,1:34:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-汤米的信  -我在这\N-Williams, Thomas.  -Yeah, over here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:35.98,1:34:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么？\NWhat you got?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:37.78,1:34:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,教育委员会来的\NBoard of Education.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:39.32,1:34:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-老小子寄出那考卷了  -看来是\N-That son of a bitch mailed it. -Likely he did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:41.75,1:34:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是要拆开  还是就这么拿着傻看？\NYou going to open it or stand there with your thumb up your butt?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:45.22,1:34:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿着傻看好些\NThumb up my butt sounds better.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:47.89,1:34:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把它还给我  你他妈的\NSkeets, come on. Give me that, you shithead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:51.56,1:34:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,福洛\NFloyd, come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:55.70,1:34:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德\NRed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:58.34,1:35:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把它丢掉  好吗？\NWill you throw that away, please?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:06.34,1:35:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狗屎  不赖\NWell, shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:20.76,1:35:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他通过了  平均丙上\NThe kid passed. C + average.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:23.76,1:35:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟你报个喜\NThought you'd like to know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:42.08,1:35:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,典狱长找你谈话\NWarden wants to talk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:57.29,1:35:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这儿？\NOut here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:58.56,1:36:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他就是这样说的\NThat's what the man said.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:16.91,1:36:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,典狱长？\NWarden?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:18.85,1:36:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汤米？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:26.29,1:36:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汤米  这次会面要你保密\NI'm asking you to keep this conversation just between us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:33.50,1:36:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我良心深感不安\NI feel awkward enough as it is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:54.22,1:36:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的判决出了问题\NWe got a situation here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:57.15,1:36:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想你明白\NI think you can appreciate that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:59.46,1:37:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:00.96,1:37:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白\NI sure can.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:02.63,1:37:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这件事真使我震惊\NI tell you, son, this thing really came along and knocked my wind out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:08.13,1:37:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我连觉都睡不好\NIt's got me up nights.That's the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:12.97,1:37:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我该怎么做才好\NThe right thing to do...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:16.47,1:37:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时连我也搞不清楚\Nsometimes it's hard to know what that is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:21.21,1:37:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你了解吗？\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:24.95,1:37:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我需要你的协助  孩子\NI need your help, son.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:27.99,1:37:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要有……\NIf I'm going to move on this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:30.49,1:37:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十足把握才能翻案\Nthere can't be the least little shred of doubt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:34.39,1:37:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我得知道\NI have to know...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:35.66,1:37:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你所说是否实话\Nif what you told Dufresne was the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:38.50,1:37:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:39.83,1:37:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,字字属实\NAbsolutely.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:41.57,1:37:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你愿在法官及陪审团前宣誓\NWould you be willing to swear before a judge and jury...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:44.77,1:37:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并且手按圣经\Nwith your hand on the Good Book...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:46.97,1:37:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在上帝跟前起誓吗？\Nand take an oath before Almighty God himself?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:49.84,1:37:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要给我这个机会\NJust give me that chance.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:55.91,1:37:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也这样想\NThat's what I thought.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:44.33,1:38:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信你已听说了\NI'm sure by now you've heard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:48.00,1:38:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真惨\NTerrible thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:50.63,1:38:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,年纪轻轻\NA man that young...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:52.44,1:38:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刑期剩下不到一年还要逃\Nless than a year to go, trying to escape.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:55.57,1:38:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,射杀他令海利伤透心\NBroke Captain Hadley's heart to shoot him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:58.81,1:39:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千真万确\NTruly, it did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:03.31,1:39:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们只有忘掉这事\NWe just have to put it behind us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:07.42,1:39:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,继续过日子\NMove on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:10.25,1:39:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到此为止\NI'm done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:13.06,1:39:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不干了\NEverything stops.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:16.66,1:39:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你找别人帮你骗钱吧\NGet someone else to run your scams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:20.26,1:39:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切照旧\NNothing stops.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:23.43,1:39:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切\NNothing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:28.01,1:39:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否则我要你生不如死\NOr you will do the hardest time there is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:31.51,1:39:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不再让警卫保护你\NNo more protection from the guards.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:34.04,1:39:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不再让你一人一间牢房  把你丢到鸡奸狂当中\NI'll pull you out of that 1 -bunk Hilton and cast you down with the sodomites.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:40.35,1:39:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日日夜夜轮奸不休\NYou'll think you've been fucked by a train.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:44.19,1:39:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,图书馆呢？\NAnd the library?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:46.36,1:39:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没了\NGone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:47.96,1:39:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用砖头封死\NSealed off, brick by brick.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:50.99,1:39:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在操场焚书\NWe'll have us a little book barbecue in the yard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:53.86,1:39:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,几里外都看得见火光\NThey'll see the flames for miles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:56.20,1:39:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家围着火跳红蕃舞\NWe'll dance around it like wild Injuns.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:00.30,1:40:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听懂了吗？\NYou understand me? Catching my drift?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:07.04,1:40:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是笨蛋吗？\NOr am I being obtuse?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:20.69,1:40:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再关他一个月  考虑清楚\NGive him another month to think about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:10.07,1:41:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老婆说她很难了解我\NMy wife used to say I'm a hard man to know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:13.94,1:41:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像一本合起来的书\NLike a closed book.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:16.58,1:41:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她整天这样抱怨\NComplained about it all the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:19.55,1:41:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她很漂亮\NShe was beautiful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:23.52,1:41:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我那么爱她\NGod, I loved her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:28.76,1:41:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是不擅表达\NI didn't know how to show it, that's all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:33.73,1:41:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我杀了她\NI killed her, Red.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:37.27,1:41:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,枪不是我开的\NI didn't pull the trigger...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:40.50,1:41:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我害她离我远去\Nbut I drove her away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:43.74,1:41:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的脾气秉性\NThat's why she died, because of me...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:46.64,1:41:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害死了她\Nthe way I am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:57.02,1:41:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你不是杀人犯\NThat don't make you a murderer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:02.23,1:42:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能说是差丈夫\NBad husband, maybe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:07.63,1:42:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以后悔  但你无罪\NFeel bad about it if you want, but you didn't pull the trigger.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:11.10,1:42:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错\NNo, I didn't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:12.84,1:42:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别人干的\NSomebody else did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:16.01,1:42:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却由我受罚\NAnd I wound up in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:20.58,1:42:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概是我命薄\NBad luck, I guess.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:26.03,1:42:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁都可能\NIt floats around.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:29.85,1:42:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沾染霉运\NIt's got to land on somebody.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:32.99,1:42:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚好轮到我\NIt was my turn, that's all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:35.59,1:42:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我被卷入龙卷风\NI was in the path of the tornado.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:44.30,1:42:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是没想到刮了这么久\NI just didn't expect the storm would last as long as it has.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:52.61,1:42:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有可能假释吗？\NThink you'll ever get out of here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:55.55,1:42:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我？\NMe?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:59.55,1:43:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有吧\NYeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:01.89,1:43:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要等我老得发须花白\NOne day, when I got a long, white beard...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:04.39,1:43:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神智不清才行\Nand two or three marbles rolling around upstairs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:09.59,1:43:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟你说我要去哪儿\NI tell you where I'd go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:12.70,1:43:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芝华塔尼欧\NZihuatanejo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:15.23,1:43:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里？\NSay what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:16.73,1:43:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芝华塔尼欧\NZihuatanejo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:19.50,1:43:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在墨西哥\NIt's in Mexico.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:22.54,1:43:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太平洋边的小地方\NA little place on the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:25.81,1:43:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-知道墨西哥人怎样说太平洋的吗？  -不知道\N-You know what the Mexicans say about the Pacific? -No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:30.41,1:43:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是没有回忆的海洋\NThey say it has no memory.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:34.38,1:43:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要在那度此余生\NThat's where I want to live the rest of my life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:38.69,1:43:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有回忆的温暖地\NA warm place with no memory.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:44.43,1:43:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在海边\NOpen up a little hotel...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:48.07,1:43:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开个小旅馆\Nright on the beach.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:50.17,1:43:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,买条破船\NBuy some worthless old boat...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:52.90,1:43:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,整修一新\Nand fix it up new.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:57.27,1:43:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,载客出海\NTake my guests out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:59.34,1:44:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包船海钓\Ncharter fishing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:04.55,1:44:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芝华塔尼欧\NZihuatanejo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:09.82,1:44:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在那地方也大有可为\NIn a place like that, I could use a man that knows how to get things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:20.23,1:44:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在外头吃不开的\NI don't think I could make it on the outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:29.74,1:44:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一生都耗在肖申克\NI been in here most of my life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:33.24,1:44:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经体制化了\NI'm an institutional man now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:35.91,1:44:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像老布\NJust like Brooks was.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:39.12,1:44:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别小看自己\NYou underestimate yourself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:41.39,1:44:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不这么认为\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:46.82,1:44:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在牢里让你有求必应\NIn here I'm the guy who can get things for you, sure, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:51.53,1:44:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一出社会  电话簿里样样有\Noutside all you need is the Yellow Pages.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:54.26,1:44:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我连查都不会查\NHell, I wouldn't know where to begin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:58.64,1:45:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太平洋？\NPacific Ocean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:00.67,1:45:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狗屁\NShit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:02.27,1:45:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大的我心都毛了\NScare me to death, something that big.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:04.67,1:45:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会\NNot me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:07.18,1:45:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老婆和她情夫不是我杀的\NI didn't shoot my wife,and I didn't shoot her lover.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:11.68,1:45:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我犯的错已还清\NWhatever mistakes I made,I've paid for them and then some.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:15.95,1:45:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一间旅店  一叶扁舟\NThat hotel, that boat...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:19.22,1:45:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要求并不过份\NI don't think that's too much to ask.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:26.36,1:45:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不该有此妄想\NYou shouldn't be doing this to yourself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:29.00,1:45:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全痴人说梦\NThis is just shitty pipe dreams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:31.47,1:45:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,墨西哥和这儿\NMexico is way down there and you're in here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:34.14,1:45:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天南地北\Nand that's the way it is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:36.04,1:45:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的没错\NYeah, right. That's the way it is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:40.38,1:45:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,远隔天涯海角\NIt's down there and I'm in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:45.35,1:45:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我猜是人就得二选一\NI guess it comes down to a simple choice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:50.99,1:45:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要么忙着活……\NGet busy living...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:53.86,1:45:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要么忙着死\Nor get busy dying.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:59.46,1:46:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪\NAndy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:04.47,1:46:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑞德\NRed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:08.00,1:46:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等你假释后  帮我个忙\NIf you ever get out of here,do me a favor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:10.94,1:46:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题  你说\NSure, Andy. Anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:15.08,1:46:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴克斯顿有个大草场  知道巴克斯顿吗？\NThere's a big hayfield up near Buxton.You know where Buxton is?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:20.42,1:46:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-那一带草场多得很  -有一处与众不同\N-A lot of hayfields up there. -One in particular.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:23.75,1:46:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那里有长石墙  北端还有大橡树\NIt's got a long rock wall with a big oak tree at the north end.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:27.89,1:46:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美得像福斯特的诗\NIt's like something out of a Robert Frost poem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:31.70,1:46:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在那儿向她求婚\NIt's where I asked my wife to marry me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:35.60,1:46:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们去野餐\NWe went there for a picnic...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:38.10,1:46:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在橡树下做爱\Nand made love under that oak...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:40.87,1:46:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我开口  她首肯\Nand I asked and she said yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:47.11,1:46:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,答应我  瑞德\NPromise me, Red.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:49.78,1:46:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你终获假释\NIf you ever get out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:51.62,1:46:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去找到那个地方\Nfind that spot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:54.28,1:46:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石墙底下有一块奇石\NAt the base of that wall, there's a rock that has no earthly business in Maine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:00.26,1:47:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑色火山玻璃石\NPiece of black, volcanic glass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:05.96,1:47:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,底下埋着给你的东西\NSomething's buried under it I want you to have.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:09.40,1:47:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么？\NWhat, Andy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:11.07,1:47:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你埋着什么？\NWhat's buried under there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:14.40,1:47:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你搬开它\NYou'll have to pry it up...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:16.47,1:47:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就知道了\Nto see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:23.65,1:47:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们听我说\NNo, I'm telling you. The guy is...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:26.25,1:47:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他胡言乱语\NHe's talking funny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:29.09,1:47:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真担心他\NI'm really worried about him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:31.19,1:47:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们要盯紧他\NLet's keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:32.82,1:47:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白天不要紧  晚上孤伶伶的\NThat's fine during the day, but at night he's all alone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:37.53,1:47:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天哪\NOh, Lord.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:40.00,1:47:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？\NWhat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:42.33,1:47:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪今天到载货区\NAndy come down to the loading dock today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:45.30,1:47:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问我要一条绳子\NHe asked me for a length of rope.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:47.60,1:47:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-绳子？  -六尺长\NRope? Six feet long.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:50.54,1:47:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你给了他？\NAnd you gave it to him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:52.78,1:47:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么不给？\NSure. Why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:54.78,1:47:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-天啊  赫伍  -我怎么想得到？\N-Jesus! Heywood. -How was I supposed to know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:59.12,1:48:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你忘了老布？\NRemember Brooks Hatlen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:00.85,1:48:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不  安迪不会寻短\NAndy would never do that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:05.22,1:48:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不会\NNever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:08.36,1:48:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁知道呢？\NI don't know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:12.53,1:48:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人的忍耐是有限度的\NEvery man has his breaking point.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:16.90,1:48:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快  我要回家\NLickety-split.Want to get home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:19.47,1:48:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上好了\NJust about finished, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:38.36,1:48:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚要存三笔\NThree deposits tonight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:47.96,1:48:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把衣物送洗\NGet my stuff down to the laundry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:50.07,1:48:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把鞋擦亮\NAnd shine my shoes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:51.90,1:48:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-要擦得雪亮  -是  先生\N-I want them looking like mirrors. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:00.34,1:49:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你回来真好  安迪\NIt's good having you back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:02.75,1:49:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有你可差多了\NPlace wasn't the same without you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:51.49,1:49:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熄灯\NLights out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.40,1:50:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也曾熬过孤寂长夜\NI've had some long nights in stir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:28.47,1:50:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,独自在心中思东想西\NAlone in the dark with nothing but your thoughts...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:31.33,1:50:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间慢得如同刀割\Ntime can draw out like a blade.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:39.34,1:50:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是我毕生最长的一夜\NThat was the longest night of my life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:58.19,1:50:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,清点人数！\NGive me a count!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:03.87,1:51:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-南三层到齐  -北四层到齐\NTier 3 south, clear!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:08.14,1:51:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,北三层到齐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:09.84,1:51:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,二层245没人\NMan missing on tier 2, cell 245!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:13.21,1:51:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杜弗伦\NDufresne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:14.81,1:51:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快出来 别耍花样\NCome out. You're holding up the show!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:20.38,1:51:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等我找上门  可就重赏你的脑袋了\NDon't make me come down or I'll thump your skull for you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:31.36,1:51:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该死  我还得等你一个  你敢耽搁我时间\NDamn it, you're putting me behind! I got a schedule to keep.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:35.40,1:51:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你最好是病了或是死了\NYou'd better be sick or dead in there. I shit you not!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:38.90,1:51:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听见没有？\NYou hear me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:46.34,1:51:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢  我的上帝\NOh, my Holy God.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:05.43,1:52:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这一分区每人都要问\NI want every man on this cellblock questioned.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:08.43,1:52:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-先从他朋友开始  -谁？\N-Start with that friend of his. -Who?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:11.17,1:52:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他\NHim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:13.57,1:52:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打开237\NOpen 237.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:18.64,1:52:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么叫“他不见了”？  这算什么鬼话？\NWhat do you mean, "He just wasn't here"? Don't say that to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:23.18,1:52:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你再说一次试试\NDon't tell me that again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:24.71,1:52:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但他真的不见了\NBut sir, he wasn't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:25.98,1:52:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没长眼睛吗？\NI can see that, Haig! Think I'm blind?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:30.12,1:52:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是这个意思？\NIs that what you're saying?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:31.72,1:52:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我眼瞎了？  -不敢  长官\N-Am I blind, Haig? -No, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:35.29,1:52:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你呢？ 你瞎了吗？\NWhat about you. You blind?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:38.29,1:52:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你说这是什么？  -昨晚的点名记录\N-Tell me what this is. -Last night's count.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:41.06,1:52:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上面明明写着杜弗伦\NYou see Dufresne's name there? I sure do. Right there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:44.57,1:52:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“杜弗伦”\N"Dufresne."
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:47.57,1:52:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熄灯时\NHe was in his cell...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:49.27,1:52:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他在牢里\Nat lights out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:50.47,1:52:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上应该也在才对\NReasonable he'd be here in the morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:53.74,1:52:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把他找到\NI want him found.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:55.58,1:52:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一刻不能拖  现在就找！\NNot tomorrow, not after breakfast. Now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:59.28,1:53:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是  长官\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:01.48,1:53:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搜人去  快点\NLet's go. Move your butts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:07.16,1:53:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站好\NStand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:09.59,1:53:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说\NWell?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:14.10,1:53:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说什么？\NWell, what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:15.30,1:53:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们俩成天粘在一起\NI see you two all the time.You're thick as thieves, you are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:19.84,1:53:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他一定说过什么\NHe must have said something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:22.07,1:53:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,报告典狱长\NNo, sir, Warden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:23.94,1:53:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有\NNot a word.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:26.78,1:53:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那真是奇迹了\NLord, it's a miracle!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:29.95,1:53:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人像屁一样凭空消失\NMan vanished like a fart in the wind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:33.18,1:53:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不见踪影\NNothing left...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:35.18,1:53:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只剩一堆石头\Nbut some damn rocks on a windowsill.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:38.12,1:53:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有墙上那骚货  问问她吧\NAnd that cupcake on the wall. Let's ask her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:41.06,1:53:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许她知道些什么\NMaybe she knows.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:43.06,1:53:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你来说  短裤妞儿\NWhat say there, fuzzy-britches? Feel like talking?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:47.23,1:53:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她不会说的\NGuess not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:49.10,1:53:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别人不说  为何她要说\NWhy should she be any different?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:52.37,1:53:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错  你们有预谋\NThis is a conspiracy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:54.67,1:53:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这样\NThat's what this is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:57.11,1:54:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个超级大阴谋\NOne big, damn conspiracy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:01.11,1:54:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每个人都有份\NAnd everyone's in on it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:03.75,1:54:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包括她\NIncluding her!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:39.95,1:54:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1966年\NIn 1966...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:41.85,1:54:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪·杜弗伦逃离……\NAndy Dufresne escaped...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:44.45,1:54:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肖申克监狱\Nfrom Shawshank Prison.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:48.26,1:54:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狱方只寻获泥渍囚衣\NAll they found was a muddy set of prison clothes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:51.46,1:54:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一块肥皂\Na bar of soap...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:53.20,1:54:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和一把石锤\Nand an old rock hammer...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:54.96,1:54:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一把几乎解体的石锤\Ndamn near worn down to the nub.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:01.94,1:55:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾夸口要花六百年才能挖通的隧道\NI had thought it'd take a man 600 years to tunnel through the wall with it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:07.34,1:55:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪花了不到20年\NOld Andy did it in less than 20.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:28.26,1:55:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他喜爱研究地质\NOh, Andy loved geology.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:31.33,1:55:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,碎石令他想一探究竟\NI imagine it appealed to his meticulous nature.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:34.90,1:55:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刑期如同\NAn ice age here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:37.17,1:55:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冰河时代\Nmillion years of mountain building there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:40.68,1:55:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地质学探讨压力及时间\NGeology is the study of pressure and time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:44.35,1:55:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是凿通的关键——\NThat's all it takes, really.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:47.08,1:55:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,压力\NPressure...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:48.82,1:55:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间\Nand time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:51.42,1:55:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和一张够大的海报\NThat and a big goddamn poster.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:57.29,1:55:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像我说的\NLike I said...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:58.96,1:56:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在牢里  没事也得找事做\Nin prison, a man will do anything to keep his mind occupied.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:05.77,1:56:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来安迪的嗜好  就是把他的牢墙\NSeems Andy's favorite hobby was toting his wall out into the exercise yard...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:11.11,1:56:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一次一把地搬到操场上\Na handful at a time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:14.34,1:56:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概就在汤米死后\NI guess after Tommy was killed...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:16.61,1:56:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪决定不再久留\NAndy decided he'd been here long enough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:19.78,1:56:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快  我要回家\NLickety-split.I want to get home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:23.09,1:56:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上就好\NI'm just about finished, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:46.58,1:56:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚要存三笔\NThree deposits tonight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:55.82,1:56:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪奉命行事\NAndy did like he was told.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:58.32,1:57:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把鞋子擦得雪亮\NBuffed those shoes to a high mirror-shine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:05.50,1:57:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,警卫都没注意\NThe guards simply didn't notice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:08.10,1:57:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也没有\NNeither did I.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:09.77,1:57:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说真的\NI mean, seriously...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:11.50,1:57:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁会注意别人的鞋子\Nhow often do you really look at a man's shoes?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:18.06,1:59:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪就这样爬向自由\NAndy crawled to freedom through 500 yards...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:21.46,1:59:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在恶臭中匍匐五百码\Nof shit-smelling foulness I can't even imagine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:25.80,1:59:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,换我才不干呢\NOr maybe I just don't want to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:32.54,1:59:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五百码\NFive hundred yards.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:35.41,1:59:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有五个足球场那么长\NThat's the length of five football fields.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:39.12,1:59:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接近半英里\NJust shy of half a mile.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:36.91,2:00:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,次日清晨  在拉寇儿坦露她的秘密之时\NThe next morning, right about the time Raquel was spilling her secret...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:41.81,2:00:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个从未现世的人\Na man nobody ever laid eyes on before...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:44.88,2:00:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走进缅因国家银行\Nstrolled into the Maine National Bank.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:48.05,2:00:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前  他不是实体\NUntil that moment, he didn't exist.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:51.79,2:00:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-只存在于文件上  -有何贵干？\N-Except on paper. -May I help you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:54.56,2:00:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他各种证件都有\NHe had all the proper ID...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:56.69,2:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驾照  出生证  社会保险卡\Ndriver's license, birth certificate, Social Security card...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:00.83,2:01:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,签名分毫不差\NAnd the signature was a spot-on match.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:03.57,2:01:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去您的生意令我真心遗憾\NI must say I'm sorry to be losing your business.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:06.87,2:01:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝您侨居愉快\NI hope you'll enjoy living abroad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:09.41,2:01:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:11.17,2:01:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定的\NI'm sure I will.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:13.24,2:01:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是银行本票  就这样吗？\NHere's your cashier's check, sir. Will there be anything else?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:16.78,2:01:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,麻烦你\NPlease.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:18.35,2:01:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮我寄出去好吗？\NWould you add this to your outgoing mail?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:21.35,2:01:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乐意之至\NI'd be happy to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:24.35,2:01:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-再会  -走好\N-Good day, sir. -Good day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:26.62,2:01:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那天上午史帝文先后去了十多家银行\NMr. Stevens visited nearly a dozen banks in the Portland area that morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:31.53,2:01:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总共加起来\NAll told, he blew town...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:33.33,2:01:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提走了诺顿37万美金\Nwith better than $370,000 of Warden Norton's money.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:38.87,2:01:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作为十九年冤狱的补偿\NSeverance pay for 19 years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:48.88,2:01:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好 这里是《波特兰号角日报》\NGood morning, Portland Daily Bugle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:43.93,2:02:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是海利吗？  你有权保持沉默\NByron Hadley? You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:47.14,2:02:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从现在起 你所说的一切 都将可能成为呈堂证供\NIf you give up this right, anything you say can be held against you in court.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:52.01,2:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当时我没有在场  后来听说\NI wasn't there to see, but I hear Byron Hadley sobbed like a girl...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:56.68,2:02:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海利被人带走的时候  哭得像个娘们儿\Nwhen they took him away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:04.05,2:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诺顿却无意乖乖就范\NNorton had no intention of going that quietly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:23.41,2:03:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诺顿\NSamuel Norton.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:24.94,2:03:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诺顿  我们有拘捕令  开门\NWe have a warrant for your arrest. Open up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:30.81,2:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把门打开\NOpen the door.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:33.75,2:03:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不清楚是哪一把\NI'm not sure which key.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:44.69,2:03:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别自找麻烦  诺顿\NMake it easy on yourself, Norton!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:58.61,2:04:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我猜他脑中最后一件事\NI like to think the last thing that went through his head...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:02.28,2:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了枪子儿\Nother than that bullet...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:04.08,2:04:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是在想安迪为何能整倒他\Nwas to wonder how the hell Andy Dufresne ever got the best of him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:11.02,2:04:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,典狱长呜呼后不久\NNot long after the warden deprived us of his company...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:14.76,2:04:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我收到一张明信片\NI got a postcard in the mail.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:18.29,2:04:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没写字  但有邮戳\NIt was blank, but the postmark said...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:21.33,2:04:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来自德州汉考克堡\NFort Hancock, Texas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:24.00,2:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汉考克堡\NFort Hancock...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:25.63,2:04:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在边境线上\Nright on the border.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:27.77,2:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪就是从那里出境的\NThat's where Andy crossed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:30.34,2:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驾着敞蓬车驶向南方\NWhen I picture him heading south in his own car with the top down...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:34.81,2:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想到这画面就令我开怀大笑\Nit always makes me laugh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:38.88,2:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪·杜弗伦\NAndy Dufresne...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:40.82,2:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爬过肮脏的下水道\Nwho crawled through a river of shit...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:43.05,2:04:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出来已焕然一新\Nand came out clean on the other side.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:46.29,2:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安迪·杜弗伦\NAndy Dufresne...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:48.46,2:04:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向太平洋驶去\Nheaded for the Pacific.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:53.03,2:04:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海利掐住他喉咙说\NHadley's got him by the throat, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:55.40,2:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“他活的不耐烦了。”\NHe says, "I believe this boy's about to have himself an accident."
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:59.40,2:05:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老友们常聊起他\NThose of us who knew him best talk about him often.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:02.94,2:05:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他那些惊人之举\NI swear, the stuff he pulled...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:04.84,2:05:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“请我朋友喝啤酒吧……”\N"My friends could use a couple of beers."
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:08.14,2:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真的做到了！\NAnd he got it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:11.05,2:05:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时我会感伤\NSometimes it makes me sad, though...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:13.72,2:05:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的离去\NAndy being gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:15.85,2:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不得不提醒自己\NI have to remind myself that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:17.05,2:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有些鸟儿是注定不会被关在牢笼里的\Nsome birds aren't meant to be caged.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:20.46,2:05:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它们的每一片羽毛都闪耀着自由的光辉\NTheir feathers are just too bright.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:24.23,2:05:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当它们盘旋飞离之时\NAnd when they fly away...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:26.40,2:05:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会由衷地祝贺它们获得自由\Nthe part of you that knows it was a sin to lock them up does rejoice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:31.87,2:05:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无奈的是\NBut still...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:33.60,2:05:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你得继续在这乏味之地苟活\Nthe place you live in is that much more drab and empty that they're gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:42.14,2:05:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真怀念这位友伴\NI guess I just miss my friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:08.97,2:06:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请坐\NPlease sit down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:15.98,2:06:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,埃利斯·博伊德·瑞丁\NEllis Boyd Redding...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:18.08,2:06:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据你的材料 你的终身监禁已经服满40年\Nyour files say you've served 40 years of a life sentence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:22.15,2:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你改过自新了吗？\NYou feel you've been rehabilitated?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:26.16,2:06:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改过自新？\NRehabilitated?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:29.76,2:06:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢  让我想想\NWell, now, let me see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:32.66,2:06:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不大明白这个词的含义\NI don't have any idea what that means.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:37.10,2:06:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说准备好重返社会\NIt means you're ready to rejoin society...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:39.94,2:06:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我当然明白你的意思  年轻人\NI know what you think it means, sonny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:44.44,2:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我而言  这只是个术语\NTo me it's just a made-up word.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:47.78,2:06:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,政客发明的术语\NA politician's word so that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:50.55,2:06:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好让你们穿西装打领带\Nyoung fellas like yourself can wear a suit and a tie...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:54.55,2:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有活干\Nand have a job.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:58.12,2:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底想了解什么？\NWhat do you really want to know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:00.99,2:07:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我后悔犯罪吗？\NAm I sorry for what I did?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:03.39,2:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你后悔吗？\NWell, are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:06.46,2:07:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没有一天不后悔\NThere's not a day goes by I don't feel regret.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:10.67,2:07:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但并非因为关在这里 也不为讨好你们\NNot because I'm in here or because you think I should.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:17.61,2:07:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回首前尘往事\NI look back on the way I was then...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:22.31,2:07:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个\Na young...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:24.58,2:07:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,犯下重罪的小笨蛋\Nstupid kid who committed that terrible crime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:31.09,2:07:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想跟他沟通\NI want to talk to him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:34.72,2:07:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我试图讲道理\NI want to try and talk some sense to him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:37.93,2:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让他明了\NTell him the way things are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:41.96,2:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我办不到\NBut I can't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:45.60,2:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个少年早就不见了\NThat kid's long gone...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:48.80,2:07:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只剩下我垂老之躯\Nand this old man is all that's left.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:52.98,2:07:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我得接受事实\NI got to live with that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:55.81,2:07:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改过自新？\NRehabilitated?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:57.88,2:07:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狗屁不通的词儿\NIt's just a bullshit word.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:00.65,2:08:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,盖章吧  别浪费我的时间\NSo you go on and stamp your forms,sonny, and stop wasting my time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:06.66,2:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告诉你一句实话\NBecause to tell you the truth...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:09.26,2:08:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我他妈的不在乎\NI don't give a shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:37.78,2:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的 小姐\NHere you go, miss.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:42.12,2:09:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以上厕所吗？\NRestroom break?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:48.96,2:09:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别一尿尿就来报告  要去就去  懂吗?\NYou don't need to ask me every time you need to go take a piss. Just go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:54.53,2:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\NYes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:06.54,2:10:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我报告了40年\NForty years I've been asking permission to piss.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:10.45,2:10:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不报告  一滴也挤不出\NI can't squeeze a drop without say-so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:16.95,2:10:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我得面对一个残酷的事实\NThere's a harsh truth to face.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:20.79,2:10:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在狱外我根本混不下去\NNo way I'm going to make it on the outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:31.57,2:10:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一心想违犯假释\NAll I do anymore is think of ways to break my parole...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:36.07,2:10:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许就能重返肖申克\Nso maybe they'd send me back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:43.75,2:10:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活在恐惧中真是糟糕\NTerrible thing, to live in fear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:47.08,2:10:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老布体会过\NBrooks Hatlen knew it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:48.95,2:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他看透了\NKnew it all too well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:52.49,2:10:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只想回到有意义的地方\NAll I want is to be back where things make sense.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:56.33,2:10:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不必整天担惊受怕\NWhere I won't have to be afraid all the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:01.06,2:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有一件事阻止了我\NOnly one thing stops me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:04.87,2:11:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我向安迪做过承诺\NA promise I made to Andy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:27.79,2:11:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了\NThere it is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:39.53,2:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常感谢您\NMuch obliged, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:20.52,2:15:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“亲爱的瑞德：”\NDear Red:
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:22.02,2:15:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“见到这封信的时候，你已经出狱了。”\NIf you're reading this,you've gotten out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:24.69,2:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“既然走了这么远的路，干脆再走远一点吧。”\Nand if you've come this far,maybe you'd come a bit further.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:29.03,2:15:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“你还记得那个地方的名字，是吗？”\NYou remember the name of the town, don't you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:33.80,2:15:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“芝华塔尼欧。”\NZihuatanejo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:36.94,2:15:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“请来帮我实现计划，”\NI could use a good man to help me get my project on wheels.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:41.04,2:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“我备妥棋盘等着你。”\NI'll keep an eye out for you, and the chessboard ready.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:45.38,2:15:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“记住，瑞德，”\NRemember, Red...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:47.12,2:15:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“心怀希望是一件好事，”\Nhope is a good thing...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:49.42,2:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“也许是最好的事。”\Nmaybe the best of things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:51.62,2:15:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“心怀希望，就永远都有希望。”\NAnd no good thing ever dies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:54.32,2:15:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“希望这封信，能让我再次见到你，”\NI will be hoping that this letter finds you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:57.39,2:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“一个健在的你。”\Nand finds you well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:59.63,2:16:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“你的朋友”\NYour friend...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:01.06,2:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“安迪”\NAndy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:36.06,2:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“要么忙着活，”\N"Get busy living...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:38.00,2:16:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“要么忙着死。”\Nor get busy dying."
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:42.60,2:16:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这话真他妈的精辟\NThat's goddamn right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:50.01,2:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是生平第二次\NFor the second time in my life...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:52.38,2:16:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又犯了罪\NI'm guilty of committing a crime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:56.02,2:16:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,违反假释出城\NParole violation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:58.62,2:17:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怀疑警方会设路障抓我\NOf course I doubt they'll toss up any roadblocks for that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:02.96,2:17:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过我这种老贼大可免了\NNot for an old crook like me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:05.19,2:17:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去德州汉考克堡  谢谢\NFort Hancock, Texas, please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:10.90,2:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我激动得不能安坐或思考\NI find I'm so excited I can barely sit still or hold a thought in my head.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:16.07,2:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想  只有真正的自由人\NI think it's the excitement only a free man can feel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:19.61,2:17:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在踏上远征那一刻  才会生出这种\NA free man at the start of a long journey...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:22.31,2:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即将揭开未来神秘面纱的激动心情吧\Nwhose conclusion is uncertain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:27.92,2:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望能顺利跨越边境\NI hope I can make it across the border.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:32.09,2:17:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望能跟重逢老友握握手\NI hope to see my friend and shake his hand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:36.99,2:17:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望太平洋如梦中一般蓝\NI hope the Pacific is as blue as it has been in my dreams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:42.90,2:17:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望……\NI hope.

